(52, 'Hetalia: World Stars', 'ヘタリア World★Stars', NULL, 'There are strange people in this world. If it is short, it will disappear for several days, and if it is long, it will disappear for hundreds of years. The name and personality changed, and suddenly appeared by someone\'s unexpected idea. Even though he is the most weird, he is loosely accepted and used by his boss. This is the story of such strange people.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: MAL News)', 0, 1, '黑塔利亚 World★Stars', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":1,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 44, 1, 5, 12, 125351, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/125351-dsXIxITtJQ4F.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(53, 'かぐや様は告らせたい～天才たちの恋愛頭脳戦～OVA', 'null', NULL, 'OVA adapting both chapters of <i>Kaguya-sama wa Kokurasetai Darkness</i> and Chapter 96 of the main series.', 3, 1, 'Kaguya-sama: Love is War OVA, Kaguya-sama wa Kokurasetai: Tensai-tachi no Renai Zunousen OVA', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":19,\"month\":5,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 452, 1, 24, 1, 125368, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx125368-QhcBkbNP0ZfU.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(54, 'The Way of the Househusband', '極主夫道', NULL, 'He was the fiercest member of the yakuza, a man who left countless underworld legends in his wake. They called him “the Immortal Dragon.” But one day he walked away from it all to travel another path—the path of the househusband! The curtain rises on this cozy yakuza comedy!\n<br><br>\n(Source: VIZ Media)', 1, 1, '[\"La Via del Grembiule\",\"Gokushufudou: Tatsu Imortal\",\"De yakuza a amo de casa\",\"La Voie du Tablier\",\"Yakuza w fartuszku. Kodeks perfekcyjnego pana domu\",\"\\u0639\\u0644\\u0649 \\u0637\\u0631\\u064a\\u0642\\u0629 \\u0631\\u0628\\u0651 \\u0627\\u0644\\u0645\\u0646\\u0632\\u0644\",\"Gokushufudou Part 1\",\"The Way of the Househusband Part 1\",\"\\u0e1e\\u0e48\\u0e2d\\u0e1a\\u0e49\\u0e32\\u0e19\\u0e2a\\u0e38\\u0e14\\u0e40\\u0e01\\u0e4b\\u0e32 \",\"\\u0e1e\\u0e48\\u0e2d\\u0e1a\\u0e49\\u0e32\\u0e19\\u0e2a\\u0e38\\u0e14\\u0e40\\u0e01\\u0e4b\\u0e32 \\u0e1', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1445, 1, 17, 5, 125426, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/125426-5BS7j1JbgaFp.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(55, 'Backflip!!', 'バクテン!!', NULL, 'Each laugh takes them higher. Each tear makes them stronger.<br>\n<br>\nThe final summer of middle school, Shoutarou Futaba discovers boys gymnastics and is completely enamored by it. Shoutarou ends up going to Soshukan Private High School (Also known as Ao High) and decides to visit the boys gymnastics club. He\'s greeted by very unique senpais and a star gymnast named Misato Ryouya. Dedicating your life to something you love during your fiery days of youth... Of course, there is frustration, and fights, but see how these boys work together as a team towards a similar goal in this drama about sports and youth. This spring, see passionate boys give their all for their youthful dreams!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 559, 1, 23, 12, 125839, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/125839-aQwXi9tJ8Q4p.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(56, 'CESTVS -The Roman Fighter-', 'セスタス -The Roman Fighter-', NULL, '54 AD. Cestus, a young boy orphaned by the Roman empire and made a slave, is placed into a training school for pugilists. It is here that he begins his journey to defy fate and fight for his own freedom.\n', 0, 1, 'Cestus: The Roman Fighter', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":15,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 38, 1, 23, 11, 125867, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx125867-M5PDaRNHN3T3.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
