(63, 'Is It Wrong to Try to Pick Up Girls in a Dungeon? III: Is It Wrong to Try to Find a Hot Spring in Orario? -Bath God Forever-', 'ダンジョンに出会いを求めるのは間違っているだろうかⅢ OVA', NULL, 'Orario has a new natural hot spring thanks to the Dian Cecht Familia, but Naaza of the Miach Familia suspects an elaborate con and needs help to prove it. That means Bell is caught in the middle of an ongoing rivalry between two Familias. Again.<br><br>(Source: HIDIVE)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":28,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 149, 1, 28, 1, 127368, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx127368-sJgXtFb4IKG2.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(64, 'Record of Ragnarok', '終末のワルキューレ', NULL, '7 million years of human civilization is coming to an end…\n<br><br>\nEvery thousand years, all the gods of the world gather in heaven to attend the Conference of Mankind Survival. The gods agree to end to mankind due to their foolish acts, but before the final verdict is made, Brunhild, the eldest of the 13 valkyrie sisters, makes an objection.\n<br><br>\n“To spice things up, why don’t you test the humans?”\n<br><br>\nShe proposes that the all-powerful gods face off in one-on-one battles against the strongest champions from human history — during a final struggle known as “Ragnarok.” The first team to win 7 out of 13 battles will be declared the winner, but it seems almost impossible for humans to win against the gods. \n<br><br>\nAlthough the gods sneer at her declaration, Brunhild provokes them further:\n<br><br>\n“Are you chickening out?”\n<br><br>\nHer words hit the gods’ nerves, and, enraged, they accept her proposal. Now, Brunhild and her sisters must choose humanity’s 13 champions in a desperate battle for survival. Will humans surpass gods and prevent humanity’s ultimate end? The eschatological battles between heaven and earth finally begins!\n<br><br>\n(Source: Warner Bros. Japan)', 3, 1, 'Shuumatsu no Walkure, معركة راغناروك, Valkyrie Apocalypse', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":17,\"month\":6,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 773, 1, 24, 12, 127399, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/127399-eiN22Xg4LG9x.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(65, 'Fortune Favors Lady Nikuko', '漁港の肉子ちゃん', NULL, '“Fortune Favors Lady Nikuko” is the heartwarming and moving comedy drama of an unconventional family – a not-so-ordinary mother-and-daughter pair who live their lives to the fullest.\n<br><br>\nEasy-going, cheerful, passionate and always ready to eat something delicious, mother Nikuko falls hard for the bad guys. Her happy motto: “Ordinary is best of all!”\nNaturally Nikuko’s loud and bold spirit embarrasses 11-year-old Kikuko, her daughter on the verge of puberty.\nWith nothing in common except living together on a boat at the port, a miracle occurs when their secret is revealed. \n', 0, 1, 'Nikuko of the Fishing Harbor', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":11,\"month\":6,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 7, 1, 97, 1, 127958, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/127958-2QhNRNjFaNB1.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(66, 'GLOOMY THE NAUGHTY GRIZZLY', 'いたずらぐまのグル～ミ～', NULL, 'GLOOMY is Pity’s pet bear. He’s a little over 6 feet and weighs as much as 2000 pomegranates. He’s well trained for the most part, but he can never remember that he’s not supposed to attack humans. Still, a pet owner must take ultimate responsibility for his pets. Recalling warm memories of GLOOMY as a cute bear cub, Pity tries to lead a life of peaceful co-existence with his pet bear.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, 'Gloomy Bear', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":12,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 13, 1, 1, 12, 128369, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx128369-a4OaoPGT8ZFP.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(67, 'しかるねこ', 'null', NULL, 'The official Twitter account for manga creator agency wwwaap\'s Shikaruneko (Angry Cat) character announced on January 5 that the character is inspiring a mini-anime. The anime will premiere this spring on TV Tokyo.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Nagging Cat', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":22,\"month\":3,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 1, 1, 1, NULL, 128394, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx128394-hNrBsBhqj50E.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(68, 'Fairy Ranmaru', 'Fairy蘭丸～あなたの心お助けします～', NULL, 'This world is all about do or die. There ain\'t no paradise. You go down once and you\'re out. This world is filled with people who suffer believing that. Hey, you there. Are you really going to pretend not to notice? We, however, cannot do that. Let us wipe away your tears. We\'ll put that smile back on your face. But it\'s not going to be for free. Please come by Bar F. Have no fear. We don\'t need any money. There\'s only one thing that we want... \"We\'ll take your heart!!\"<br><br>(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, 'F-Ran, F蘭丸', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 69, 1, 24, 12, 128399, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/128399-RuTQsN0B0cpT.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(69, 'Vivy -Fluorite Eye\'s Song-', 'Vivy -Fluorite Eye’s Song-', NULL, 'An AI named Matsumoto appears before Vivy, the world’s first autonomous humanoid AI. Matsumoto’s mission is to rewrite history together with Vivy, in order to stop the war between AI and humans that will happen one century later.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 3, 1, 'ヴィヴィ -フローライトアイズソング-', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 3459, 1, 23, 13, 128546, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/128546-V5KVgbzQwFYm.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(70, 'ODDTAXI', 'オッドタクシー', NULL, 'The taxi driver Odokawa lives a very mundane life. He has no family, doesn\'t really hang out with others, and he\'s an oddball who is narrow-minded and doesn\'t talk much. The only people he can call his friends are his doctor, Gouriki and his classmate from high school, Kakibana.<br>\n<br>\nAll of his patrons seem to be slightly odd themselves. The college student who wants the world to notice him online, Kabasawa. A nurse with secrets named Shirakawa. A comedy duo that just can\'t catch a break named the Homosapiens. A local hoodlum named Dobu. An idol group that\'s just starting out named Mystery Kiss... All these mundane conversations somehow eventually lead to a girl who\'s gone missing.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 2, 1, 'Необычное такси', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 2635, 1, 24, 13, 128547, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/128547-aVWJmZz9dwJJ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
