(85, 'Sushi Sumo', 'どすこいすしずもう', NULL, 'Sushi have become sumo wrestlers!! Which SUSHI ingredient is the strongest of all!?\n<br><br>\nTamago-nosato, Otoro-yama, Salmon-zakura, Kurumaebi-zou, Ikura-maru……and so many more.\n<br><br>\nEach unique sumo wrestler uses its ingredients to its advantage, unleashing a wide range of techniques.\n<br><br>\nSo, who will win today’s match!? Put some spirit into it!\n<br><br>\n“Hakkeyoi Nokotta!”', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":11,\"month\":3,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 1, 1, 5, NULL, 130442, '2021-11-30 10:54:34', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/130442-FMmNB5bAQrfw.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
