(101, 'Heaven\'s Design Team: Idea 13', '天地創造デザイン部 特別編', NULL, 'Episode 13 that was streamed exclusively on Amazon.<br><br>This time God\'s order is to \"make five animals and combine all of them in the end\". The designers are stumped by this ultra unreasonable and difficult order. They each work their respective strengths and after some trial and error... What exactly is the animal they created...?!<br><br>(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, 'Tenchi Souzou Design-bu Episode 13, Heaven\'s Design Team Episode 13', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 22, 1, 24, 1, 131866, '2021-11-30 10:54:35', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx131866-M3Zs2g7gkSQU.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
