(108, '青い羽みつけた！', 'null', NULL, 'The story centers on Haru and Hina, two siblings who live in the city and get along well. One day they find a beautiful blue feather on the road, and they set out to find its owner. A mysterious crow appears before them, and acts as a guide. The three then go on a journey to find the owner, meeting various birds along the way.<br><br>(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":26,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, NULL, 6, 132527, '2021-11-30 10:54:35', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx132527-GaTiOBNUQoT3.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
