(110, '七ヶ浜でみつけた', 'null', NULL, '<i>Shichigahama de Mitsuketa</i> is a 20-minute animated short based on the March 11, 2011 earthquake and resulting tsunami that struck Japan one decade ago. The anime conveys lessons learned from the earthquake and the 10-year history of Shichigahama\'s reconstruction.  \n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'I Found it in Shichigahama', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":3,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 2, 1, 20, 1, 133138, '2021-11-30 10:54:35', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/133138-coFVyi7ALUGv.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
