(121, 'ハイパーポジティブよごれモン', 'null', NULL, 'A collaboration between FIREBUG, Fuji TV, and Bandai: <i>Hyper Positive Yogoremon</i> centers on Otarou, a creature themed around dirt known as a yogoremon. It and other yogoremon will ask the meaning of words and explain negative terms in positive ways. The shorts are also posted on the official CreepHyp YouTube channel.\n<br><br>\n(Source: ANN, edited)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2021, '{\"day\":18,\"month\":4,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1, 1, 2, 12, 137333, '2021-11-30 10:54:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx137333-Q1uEQubw3SmJ.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
