(190, 'TONIKAWA: Over The Moon For You ~SNS~', 'トニカクカワイイ ～SNS～', NULL, 'When Nasa is suddenly called in for some work, Tsukasa spends her first night alone since their marriage began. As the loneliness pulls at her, she takes the smartphone that Nasa got her as a gift in hand and continues to wait. Messaging allows the two of them to stay connected, even while separated. <br><br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 3, 1, 'Tonikaku Kawaii OVA, TONIKAWA OVA, Tonikaku Kawaii Episode 13', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":18,\"month\":8,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 487, 1, 24, 1, 127371, '2021-11-30 11:11:05', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/127371-HSaCdJXeQX24.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(191, 'The Honor at Magic High School', '魔法科高校の優等生', NULL, 'Nearly a century after magic was recognized as a real form of technology, Miyuki Shiba begins her term at Magic High School. An “honor” student, she dreamed of enjoying school with her older brother Tatsuya, an “irregular” student. But a rift between the gifted Course 1 students and the inferior Course 2 students could stand in the way. This time, Miyuki is the star of the show!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 0, 1, 'The Honor Student at Magic High School', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 259, 1, 24, 13, 127688, '2021-11-30 11:11:05', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx127688-WDZFupRhW3eX.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
