(195, 'The Detective Is Already Dead', '探偵はもう、死んでいる。', NULL, 'Thwarting a hijacking with the beautiful, silver-haired detective, Siesta, transforms Kimihiko’s young life. Their success kicks off years of crime-solving and confronting syndicates around the world—until Siesta dies. Left with questions, Kimihiko moves on. But now, a new case may open healed wounds as it connects to an assassin, a world conspiracy, and his dead partner!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: The first episode aired with a runtime of ~46 minutes as opposed to the standard 24 minute long episode.</i>\n\n', 3, 1, 'La detective esta muerta., Tanmoshi, 侦探已经，死了, 侦探已死, นักสืบตายแล้ว', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1075, 1, 24, 12, 128712, '2021-11-30 11:11:05', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/128712-ten1GvlORgaw.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(196, 'The Seven Deadly Sins: Cursed by Light', '七つの大罪 光に呪われし者たち', NULL, 'Meliodas and his friends jump back into action when the new era of peace is threatened by a powerful magical alliance that could spell the end for all.', 1, 1, 'Los siete pecados capitales: La maldición de la luz, ศึกตํานาน 7 อัศวิน: สาปแห่งแสง', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 183, 1, 80, 1, 128740, '2021-11-30 11:11:05', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx128740-RP0XcDxehYQO.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(198, 'The Duke of Death and His Maid', '死神坊ちゃんと黒メイド', NULL, 'How can you fall in love when you can’t even hold hands? Due to a childhood curse, anything that the Duke touches will die—which makes his flirty maid’s behavior all the more shocking! Is there a way for the Duke and his companions to somehow break the curse, or is he doomed to a life where love is forever out of his reach?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 2, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 719, 1, 24, 12, 129277, '2021-11-30 11:11:05', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/129277-qlbNHKGvfr8f.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(199, 'I, Tsushima', '俺、つしま', NULL, 'The story centers on a woman who is getting on in years, but all her cats think she\'s a man so they call her Ojii-chan. One day a brazen cat named Tsushima appears in Ojii-chan\'s yard.', 0, 1, 'I\'m Tsushima the Cat', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 41, 1, 2, 12, 130392, '2021-11-30 11:11:05', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx130392-4Wpdaq4W5XMB.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(200, 'RE-MAIN', 'RE-MAIN（リメイン）', NULL, 'Just after winning a national water polo title in his third year of junior high, a car accident left Minato Kiyomizu in a coma. Nearly a year passes before he awakes, but with no memory of his last school year. Now in high school with a fresh start, he leaves the sport behind, but a promise has him returning to it. However, his new team is weak, and that’s just a sign for more problems to come.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 388, 1, 23, 12, 130549, '2021-11-30 11:11:05', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/130549-CIF5woRcKNET.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(202, 'The Ancient Magus\' Bride: The Boy from the West and the Knight of the Blue Storm', '魔法使いの嫁 西の少年と青嵐の騎士', NULL, 'Gabriel is an ordinary boy who just moved from London and was bored with his surrounding, until one day, he saw a wisp of purple smoke from the window of his house. At that time, he hurriedly chased the smoke, looking for any kind of freedom and fun. Though they should not, the world of boys and wizards soon intersect...<br>\n<br>\nMeanwhile, in the middle of an uncommon regular day, where Elias is helping Chise prepare to head to the college, Spriggan arrives at the mansion on a seemingly creepy horse with a grim message, \"the appearance of the ghost hunting corps. this time is very odd\".<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)<br>\n<br>\n<i> Note: The episodes were bundled with volumes 16-18 of the manga.</i>', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":9,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 125, 1, NULL, 3, 130713, '2021-11-30 11:11:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx130713-lNFzX4Hz3Fp7.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(203, 'D_CIDE TRAUMEREI THE ANIMATION', 'D_CIDE TRAUMEREI THE ANIMATION', NULL, 'The story takes place in Shibuya.<br>\n<br>\nRyuuhei had always looked up to his older brother as a child. Even after witnessing his mysterious death, Ryuuhei grows up to be a cheerful high school student. One day after his daily kickboxing practice, he is bitten by a strange creature calling itself Tris. That night, an unusual dream bothers his sleep. As the rumored \"Drops\" circulate around the city, Ryuuhei is confronted with a force of twisted desire. What is it that awaits him beyond that?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, 'ディーサイドトロイメライ', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 41, 1, 24, 13, 130997, '2021-11-30 11:11:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/130997-evCBQALxkMfb.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
