(205, 'Scarlet Nexus', 'SCARLET NEXUS', NULL, 'Solar calendar year 2020: grotesque organisms called Others have begun eating people. To take down this new enemy, the Other Suppression Force is formed. Saved by this elite team as a child, psychokinetic Yuito withstands the training to enlist. On the other hand, prodigy Kasane was scouted for her abilities. But Kasane’s dreams tell her strange things, dragging the two into an unavoidable fate.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 3, 1, 'スカーレットネクサス, 绯红结系', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":1,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 252, 1, 24, 26, 131150, '2021-11-30 11:11:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/131150-VGKhcrlNg3s2.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(206, 'The Case Study of Vanitas', 'ヴァニタスの手記', NULL, 'It’s 19th-century Paris, and young vampire Noé hunts for the Book of Vanitas. Attacked by a vampire driven insane, a human intercedes, rescues Noé, and heals the sick creature. Commanding the book and calling himself Vanitas, this doctor tempts Noé with a mad crusade to “cure” the entire vampire race. Allying with one who wields arcane power so easily may be dangerous, but does he have a choice?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 5, 1, 'Vanitas no Karte, Les Mémoires de Vanitas, 瓦尼塔斯的手记', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 2203, 1, 23, 12, 131646, '2021-11-30 11:11:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/131646-ewbYrSfyUyp6.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(207, 'Obey Me!', 'Obey Me!', NULL, 'Lucifer, Satan, and the other five princes of hell are students at the Royal Academy of Diavolo, where they train to rule the Demon World. From following humans to falling in love, their individual quirks land them in interesting situations every single day! Will their antics get them expelled, or will one of these infamous brothers come out on top?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 1, 1, 'おべいみー', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":16,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 341, 1, 5, NULL, 131880, '2021-11-30 11:11:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/131880-D64tfKTtjAEY.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(208, 'Sonny Boy', 'Sonny Boy', NULL, 'It’s an ordinary summer vacation...except for the fact that Nagara’s high school has mysteriously drifted into another dimension. As the students begin to develop strange new powers, will they work together to survive the alien environment and find a way home, or will their newly formed factions and rivalries turn on each other? <br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: The first episode received an advance release on YouTube on June 19, 2021. The regular TV broadcast started on July 16, 2021.</i>', 5, 1, 'サニーボーイ', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":16,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1268, 1, 25, 12, 132126, '2021-11-30 11:11:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/132126-urIgfuSxmxza.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
