(230, 'I, Tsushima (ONA)', '俺、つしま (ONA)', NULL, 'Web anime of <i>Ore, Tsuhima</i> that is concurrently released during the TV shorts\' broadcast, streamed on the Asmik Ace YouTube Channel.<br><br>\nOne day, “Ojiichan(woman)” who likes cats meets a talking(?) cat on the street!<br>\nThe name of the brazen cat who was originally a stray cat is “Tsushima.” “Zun,” Ojiichan’s house cat, “Chaa,” who’s spoiled and cowardly, and “Osamu,” a self-centered gangster cat have already been living in Ojiichan’s house, and Tsushima now lives together with them in peace.\nWanna take a look at the wild life of Tsushima and Ojiichan that’s filled with love for cats?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: YouTube video description)', 0, 1, 'I\'m Tsushima the Cat', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 9, 1, 2, NULL, 136512, '2021-11-30 11:11:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx136512-7nQbfsBBIHUm.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
