(253, 'Atelier Ryza: Animated Shorts', '【ライザのアトリエ】ショートアニメ', NULL, 'Short films made with RiBLA Studio, the VR tool that lets anybody make their own anime. ', 0, 1, 'Atelier Ryza', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":14,\"month\":7,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 2, 1, 2, 7, 140099, '2021-11-30 11:11:07', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b140099-DIelsgo7D6EO.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(254, 'Blink in the Desert', 'Blink in the Desert', NULL, 'Malice comes up abruptly. As if it is blinking. Capricious like a flapping insect. One day a young hermit finds a winged insect and crushes it out of disgust. Meanwhile, the elephant sees the whole situation but says nothing. From that day on, the boy is chased by shadows of the winged insects. ', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":null,\"month\":8,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1, 1, 10, 1, 140114, '2021-11-30 11:11:07', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx140114-2Lq8Fvvb73gk.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(255, '100 Years of Work in Japan', '\"働く\"の100年史', NULL, 'It\'s been almost 100 years since the \"salaryman\" type of office worker first appeared in Japan back in the 1920s.<br>\n<br>\nAs our society faces a major turning point, SmartHR decided to create a brand film to reflect upon how work styles have changed with time over the past century.<br>\n<br>\nWe hope that by looking back on history, we inspire people to think about how they want to work going forward.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Official YouTube channel)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2021, '{\"day\":18,\"month\":8,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 2, 1, 140882, '2021-11-30 11:11:07', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b140882-PGlyYvG4bNco.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(301, 'メガトン級ムサシ', 'null', NULL, 'The story takes place after 90 percent of humanity wiped out due to an invasion. Survivors live in a shelter where their lives are monitored, and memories of the invasion erased. Three teenagers from the shelter are chosen to pilot three machines that combine to form the Musashi robot, made out of a material named Megatronium alloy. The series will balance robot action with school life.', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":1,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 30, 1, NULL, NULL, 87502, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx87502-IukO9bOX8G7V.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(302, 'EUREKA／交響詩篇エウレカセブン ハイエボリューション', 'null', NULL, '', 0, 1, 'Koukyoushihen Eureka Seven Hi-Evolution 3', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":26,\"month\":11,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 29, 1, NULL, 1, 98471, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx98471-i813DFIJJHTR.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(303, 'Shikizakura', 'シキザクラ', NULL, 'Kakeru Miwa is an otherwise ordinary high school student, but a strange twist puts him on the front line in a supernatural battle against the menacing Oni. With the help of a fantastically powerful battle suit known as “Yoroi”, Kakeru joins an elite team that fights the monstrous Oni and defends humanity from otherworldly threats. The team is assigned to protect Oka Myojin, a shrine maiden who is prophesized to save the world, but she must perform a sacred ritual within Shikizakura, the horizon that connects the spiritual and physical world that lies somewhere amid the blooming cherry blossoms and the colorful autumn leaves. But in this world, the journey to destiny is hard-fought, winding and sometimes deadly.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 29, 1, 23, 12, 105119, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx105119-DIxyYkAcvjN6.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(304, 'Blade Runner: Black Lotus', 'BLADE RUNNER — BLACK LOTUS', NULL, 'Los Angeles 2032. A young woman wakes up with no memories and possessing deadly skills. The only clues to her mystery are a locked data device and a tattoo of a black lotus. Putting together the pieces, she must hunt down the people responsible for her brutal and bloody past to find the truth of her lost identity.<br></br>(Source: Crunchyroll)', 4, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":11,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 36, 1, 30, 13, 105931, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/105931-gztLVwv3SjoV.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(305, 'SAKUGAN', 'サクガン', NULL, 'In the distant future, humankind lives shoulder-to-shoulder in a cramped \"Colony\" divided by bedrock. Outside the colony extends a dangerous undeveloped area known as \"The Labyrinth.\" Those who risk their lives to explore the Labyrinth and mark undeveloped areas are known as \"Markers.\" Memempu is a young girl who wants to become a Marker, and Gagumber is a man who quit being a Marker. This rag-tag father and daughter team are about to take on the Labyrinth! \"If there is no path, then dig one!\n<br><br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)\n<br><br>\n<i>Note: Episode 1 had an early screening during Virtual Crunchyroll Expo 2021 on August 5, 2021.</i>', 9, 1, 'Sakugan Labyrinth Marker, Sacks&Guns!!, Project Anima', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 133, 1, 24, 12, 108987, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/108987-eAxLtmW3TIe6.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(306, 'MUTEKING THE Dancing HERO', 'MUTEKING THE Dancing HERO', NULL, 'Anything can happen in Neo San Francisco: monster attacks, retro-future tech, town-thumping tunes! When these monsters threaten to harsh the vibe of this city, DJ pumps up the jams to transform Muteki into Muteking, the dancing hero. The invaders can’t keep up when this superhero hits the dance floor. The classic anime retakes the stage!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 9, 1, 24, 12, 109745, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx109745-W4NnQxYpGJJO.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(307, 'Super Crooks', 'スーパー・クルックス', NULL, 'One last heist. That\'s what they all say, right? Just one final score, and everyone can retire and take up fishing. Thing is, the jails are filled with super villains who thought the same thing, and got busted. But the Heat\'s in a jam. He\'s run up the kind of gambling debt that - if he can\'t pay it back in cash - will be paid in blood. Nobody wants to see the most beloved supercrook of all time rubbed out by the mob - especially his biggest fan, Johnny Bolt. And Johnny\'s got a plan to help the Heat and make all his buddies disgustingly rich at the same time. Unfortunately for Johnny\'s recruits, they have to head to Spain and rob the world\'s most notorious super villain blind. And that\'s where things get tricky.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Millar World)', 31, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":25,\"month\":11,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 24, 1, 25, 13, 109946, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/109946-kqAu0lDwwJJY.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(308, '宇宙戦艦ヤマト2205 新たなる旅立ち 前章 -TAKE OFF- ', 'null', NULL, 'The first film in a duology of <i>Uchuu Senkan Yamato 2205: Aratanaru Tabidachi</i>.', 0, 1, 'Space Battleship Yamato 2205: A New Journey Part I: Take Off, Star Blazers', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 8, 1, NULL, 1, 112019, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx112019-oL6Tk6iPoWVf.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(309, 'Muv-Luv Alternative', 'マブラヴ オルタネイティヴ', NULL, 'A story of the bonds between those who fight, in a world pushed to its limits. On one of the countless parallel worlds that exist throughout spacetime, humanity has fought a decades long war against the BETA, hostile extraterrestrial invaders, using humanoid fighting machines called Tactical Surface Fighters. This is a story of how humanity lives and dies while on the brink of extinction…<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 2, 1, 'Muv-Luv Alternative The Animation', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 82, 1, 23, 12, 112716, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/112716-ljFnJHSIbChB.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(310, 'Ranking of Kings', '王様ランキング', NULL, 'Unable to hear, speak, or wield a sword, Prince Bojji doesn’t seem like a typical heir to the throne—and his kingdom agrees. But his fateful encounter with Kage, a shadow on the ground, gives him his first true friend. The two set off on a grand adventure and, together, form a bond that can overcome any obstacle...even being king.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 37, 1, 'King Ranking', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":15,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 706, 1, 23, 23, 113717, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113717-XFiGSPtNJQWv.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(311, 'The Vampire Dies in No Time', '吸血鬼すぐ死ぬ', NULL, 'Legendary vampire hunter Ronaldo finds an unlikely (and unwilling) ally in Draluc, the world’s weakest vampire who turns to dust at the slightest attack. Together they’re in for more hilarious misadventures than you can shake a stake at, including enemy vampires, axe-wielding editors, and other pains in the neck.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 47, 1, 'เจ้าแวมไพร์ พันธุ์ตายไว', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 136, 1, 24, 12, 118103, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/118103-ezW2oJ9T49BJ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(312, '劇場版マクロスΔ 絶対LIVE!!!!!!', 'null', NULL, 'Walküre and Delta Flight used music to save people from the Vár Syndrome, a previously unknown disease that made humans and others go berserk. However, they find themselves facing a new threat…<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Macross Delta Movie: Zettai LIVE!!!!!!, Macross Delta Movie: Absolute LIVE!!!!!!, Macross Δ Movie: Absolute LIVE!!!!!!', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 19, 1, NULL, 1, 118126, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx118126-kcHtcMuSH3P6.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(313, '神在月のこども', 'null', NULL, 'The story takes place in the town of Izumo, in Shimane prefecture, a place steeped in folklore and ancestral traditions.\n<br><br>\nAmong them is the myth of Kamiari, which has given rise over the centuries to a series of celebrations that take place in October. Formerly, the month of October was called \"Kannazuki\" (\"the month without gods\") but in Izumo, it is called \"Kamiarizuki\" (\"month of the gods\") because it is considered that during this time of the year , a myriad of deities gather for a pilgrimage to the city\'s sanctuary.\n<br><br>\nAt the heart of this place lives Kanna, a young girl passionate about racing who suddenly loses all her motivation when her mother dies.', 0, 1, 'Child of Kamiari Month', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 19, 1, NULL, 1, 118390, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx118390-xt9ec1JIBSgv.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(314, 'My Senpai is Annoying', '先輩がうざい後輩の話', NULL, 'Being seen as a full-fledged business woman isn’t easy for Futaba Igarashi when her senpai, Harumi, treats her like a kid. Days for her are never typical, at work or outside of it, with all the antics going on in her life. As mishaps ensue, she’ll find herself growing closer with her loudmouth senpai. Maybe Futaba feels more than she lets on, but one thing’s for sure: she’s still annoyed!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 55, 1, 'ลุ้นรักรุ่นน้องตัวจิ๋วกับรุ่นพี่ตัวป่วน', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 516, 1, 24, 12, 120646, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/120646-RsYJHXzMdnXp.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(316, 'Yuki Yuna is a Hero: The Great Mankai Chapter', '結城友奈は勇者である-大満開の章-', NULL, 'The third season of <i>Yuuki Yuuna wa Yuusha de Aru</i>.<br>\n<br>\nThe magical girls of the Sanshu Middle School Hero Club have one goal: to make people smile whenever they can and to always help those in need. Through teamwork and the help of their magical powers, Yuna, Mimori, Fuu, Itsuki, Karin and Sonoko have vanquished deadly Vertexes, recovered a missing friend and balanced their lives as magical girls and regular middle school students. Now a new adventure begins, one that will test their skills and their bond as friends alike.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)', 3, 1, 'Yuki Yuna is a Hero Season 3', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 59, 1, 24, 12, 122292, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/122292-lDCKcE35BOVo.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(317, 'Sing a Bit of Harmony', 'アイの歌声を聴かせて', NULL, 'The film tells the story of a new transfer student interested in her surroundings, and a song that brings happiness to her and her classmates.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 3, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":29,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 74, 1, NULL, 1, 123899, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx123899-AimlRWzAqpHC.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(318, 'Sword Art Online the Movie -Progressive- Aria of a Starless Night', '劇場版 ソードアート・オンライン プログレッシブ 星なき夜のアリア', NULL, '\"There\'s no way to beat this game. The only difference is when and where you die...\"<br>\n<br>\nOne month has passed since Akihiko Kayaba\'s deadly game began, and the body count continues to rise. Two thousand players are already dead.<br>\n<br>\nKirito and Asuna are two very different people, but they both desire to fight alone. Nonetheless, they find themselves drawn together to face challenges from both within and without. Given that the entire virtual world they now live in has been created as a deathtrap, the surviving players of Sword Art Online are starting to get desperate, and desperation makes them dangerous to loners like Kirito and Asuna. As it becomes clear that solitude equals suicide, will the two be able to overcome their differences to find the strength to believe in each other, and in doing so, survive?<br>\n<br>\n<i>Sword Art Online: Progressive</i> is a new version of the Sword Art Online tale that starts at the beginning of Kirito and Asuna\'s epic adventure—on the very first level of the deadly world of Aincrad!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Yen Press)', 1, 1, 'SAO Progressive, Sword Art Online: Progressive - อาเรียแห่งคืนที่ไร้ดาว', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":30,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 705, 1, 97, 1, 124140, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/124140-rkA3sbYSFSo9.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(319, 'Baki Hanma', '範馬刃牙', NULL, 'To gain the skills he needs to surpass his powerful father, Baki enters Arizona State Prison to take on the notorious inmate known as Mr. Unchained.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Netflix)', 6, 1, 'Baki: Son of Ogre, Hanma Baki: SON OF OGRE', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":30,\"month\":9,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 220, 1, 24, 12, 124195, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx124195-5Z1JSrRlbMRe.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(320, 'フラ・フラダンス', 'null', NULL, 'The story centers on Hiwa Natsunagi, a novice at hula dancing who nevertheless takes a job as a hula dancer at the real life Spa Resort Hawaiians hotel. The film shows the relationships between her and her colleagues.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":12,\"year\":2021}', 'NOT_YET_RELEASED', 10, 1, 110, 1, 125841, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx125841-UODyqabwgKEb.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(321, '映画 すみっコぐらし 青い月夜のまほうのコ', 'null', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '映画すみっコぐらし2, Eiga Sumikko Gurashi 2', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":null,\"month\":11,\"year\":2021}', 'NOT_YET_RELEASED', 1, 1, NULL, 1, 125931, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx125931-yS9UvZoFLjSQ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(322, 'Banished from the Hero’s Party, I Decided to Live a Quiet Life in the Countryside', '真の仲間じゃないと勇者のパーティーを追い出されたので、辺境でスローライフすることにしました', NULL, 'A heroic and mighty adventurer dreams of...opening a pharmacy?<br>\n<br>\nRed was once a part of the Hero’s party, a group destined to save the world by fighting the Raging Demon Lord. But after being betrayed by his comrade, Red hopes to start anew by opening a small apothecary in a sleepy town on the frontier. While keeping his past life a secret is the goal, it won’t be easy...especially when a beautiful adventurer from his past asks to move in.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 21, 1, 'Banished from the Heroes\' Party, I Decided to Live a Quiet Life in the Countryside, ผมโดนกลุ่มผู้กล้าขับไส เลยต้องไปสโลว์ไลฟ์ที่ชายแดน', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 483, 1, 24, 13, 126213, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/126213-1nOONZyGeIfR.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(323, 'Ancient Girl’s Frame', '闘神機ジーズフレーム', NULL, 'At the end of the 21st century, the discovery of a new energy source called \"DG energy\" (short for \"divine grace energy\") has revolutionized Earth\'s economy and allowed humanity to colonize space. However, when the initial expedition reaches Pluto, they are attacked by a mysterious, giant life-form known as \"Nergal.\"\n<br><br>\nThe Earth Alliance Army fights back by creating an \"AG Unit\" using ancient robot weapons known as the \"G\'s Frame\" which were excavated from archaeological sites all around the world. Girls with special qualities known as \"Ancient Girls\" can pilot these robots against the Nergal. However, the first AG Unit suffers heavy casualties in the Jupiter Trojan campaign, and the pilot of Unit 04, Minamiya Reiu, goes missing-in-action...\n<br><br>\nYears later, Minamiya Reika, the younger sister of Reiu, enlists with the AG Unit to search for her sister and to protect the Earth from the Nergal. A story of friendship, ancient robot weapons, and battles to the death with the Nergal ensues.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll News)', 1, 1, '斗神姬, Doushenji', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":11,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 10, 1, 24, 24, 126393, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx126393-PZNOgphwHn4J.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(324, 'Selection Project', 'SELECTION PROJECT', NULL, 'Suzune Miyama has been sick since childhood, but always used idol Akari Amasawa’s music for courage and smiles through hard times. Now in her final year of junior high, Suzune is auditioning against thousands of contestants to become one of nine chosen idols in the “Selection Project”—the exact audition competition Akari used to gain fame. Will she follow in her icon’s footsteps?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 10, 1, 'selepro', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":1,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 100, 1, 24, 13, 126790, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/126790-Lb1tXO0ohTZY.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(325, 'PuraOre! ~Pride of Orange~', 'プラオレ！～PRIDE OF ORANGE～', NULL, 'Manaka’s competitive spirit ignites when she discovers ice hockey! Even though she’s a rookie, she’s got her sights set on Nikko City’s hockey team, where girls aim for the top as they compete in this full-contact sport. After finally convincing her childhood friends and her sister to play, they join a team of girls ready to go for the goal!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 4, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 36, 1, 24, 12, 126793, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx126793-L29Tdzt6NDeQ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(326, 'The Night Beyond the Tricornered Window', 'さんかく窓の外側は夜', NULL, 'Bookstore employee Mikado always had a tendency to see creepy things. He had lived his life pretending he didn\'t see these things but then he has a fateful encounter with an exorcist named Hiyakawa. Mikado ends up being forced to help out with exorcism duties and has to deal with the embarrassing fact that exorcising these things with Hiyakawa somehow feels really good. While getting dragged into dealing with these cases every day, they run into a cold-blooded murder case.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 17, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 87, 1, 24, 12, 126897, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/126897-xNk8oIDPRNy7.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(327, 'World Trigger 3rd Season', 'ワールドトリガー 3rdシーズン', NULL, 'The third season of <i>World Trigger</i>.<br>\n<br>\nWith Hyuse joining the Tamakoma Squad, the rank wars are continuing and the Tamakoma squad are striving to get selected for the Away Missions. \n\n\n', 10, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 164, 1, 23, 12, 127400, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx127400-m2xz2qDVqQwL.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(328, 'Platinum End', 'プラチナエンド', NULL, 'When life becomes too much for Mirai to bear and attempts taking his own life, he’s saved by Nasse, a guardian angel who offers him a chance at becoming the new god. To do so, he must face off against 12 other candidates within 999 days. Mirai, who was once at rock bottom, now finds himself with supernatural powers in a battle royale for the highest title.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 42, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 767, 1, 24, 24, 127401, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/127401-e27CVSLfGjnb.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(329, 'Taisho Otome Fairy Tale', '大正オトメ御伽話', NULL, 'Shima Tamahiko is a self-proclaimed pessimist who hates the world, and with good reason—he’s been exiled to the countryside by his wealthy family because of his disability. But his lonely life is turned upside down by the arrival of Tachibana Yuzuki, his arranged bride. Her cheerfulness slowly heals Shima’s heart in this slice of life romance set during the Taisho era.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 14, 1, 'เรื่องเล่าของสาวน้อยยุคไทโช', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 215, 1, 24, 12, 127412, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/127412-0xcienOq4Tls.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
