(331, 'Mushoku Tensei: Jobless Reincarnation Cour 2', '無職転生 ～異世界行ったら本気だす～ 第2クール', NULL, 'Rudeus, Eris, and Rujierd head for Asura Kingdom in search of answers. Meanwhile, Roxy sets out across the Demon Continent to find Rudeus.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Funimation, edited)', 180, 1, 'Mushoku Tensei: Jobless Reincarnation Part 2, ชาตินี้พี่ต้องเทพ พาร์ท 2', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 2577, 1, 24, 12, 127720, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/127720-oBpHiMWQhFVN.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(332, 'Blue Period', 'ブルーピリオド', NULL, 'The studious Yatora leaves a dry life of study and good manners behind for a new passion: painting. But untethering yourself from all your past expectations is dangerous as well as thrilling…\n<br><br>\n(Source: Kodansha USA)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: The anime received an early premiere on Netflix on Sep 25, 2021. The regular TV broadcast started on Oct 2, 2021.</i>', 48, 1, 'Periodo Azul', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":25,\"month\":9,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 997, 1, 24, NULL, 128705, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/128705-x78UTJPCbqbd.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
