(336, 'プリンセス・プリンシパル Crown Handler 第2章', 'null', NULL, 'The second out of six movie sequels to the TV series.', 0, 1, 'Princess Principal Movie 2', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":23,\"month\":9,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 17, 1, 60, 1, 129759, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx129759-4ZQ5MPyE52Py.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(337, 'Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba 2', '鬼滅の刃２', NULL, 'The second season of <i>Kimetsu no Yaiba</i>.<br>\n<br>\n<i>Notes:<br>\n- The first seven episodes of this entry is the TV version of Kimetsu no Yaiba: Mugen Ressha-hen.<br>\n- The first episode (10 October) is entirely anime original.<br>\n- The eighth episode (5 December) airs with a runtime of ~1 hour.</i>', 111, 1, 'Kimetsu no Yaiba: Mugen Ressha-hen, Kimetsu no Yaiba: Yuukaku-hen, Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Entertainment District Arc, Demon Slayer -Kimetsu no Yaiba Mugen Train, 鬼滅の刃 遊郭編, 鬼滅の刃 無限列車編, ดาบพิฆาตอสูร ภาค 2, Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba - Le quartier des plaisirs', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 2314, 1, 23, NULL, 129874, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/129874-XNlp0QqyzZO5.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(338, 'The World\'s Finest Assassin Gets Reincarnated in Another World as an Aristocrat', '世界最高の暗殺者、異世界貴族に転生する', NULL, 'The world\'s number one assassin has been reincarnated as the eldest son of a family of aristocrat assassins. In exchange for being reincarnated in another world, a goddess has imposed upon him one condition. \"Kill the Hero who is prophesied to destroy the world.\" <br>\n<br>\nThis was to be the mission in his new life. The synergistic effect of the vast knowledge and experience he gained that made all manner of assassinations possible in the modern world, and the secret techniques and magic of the fantasy world\'s most powerful family of assassins turn him into the greatest assassin of all time.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 36, 1, 'Ansatsu Kizoku, สุดยอดมือสังหาร อวตารมาต่างโลก', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 1062, 1, 24, 12, 129898, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/129898-Qp41lxD3wU9e.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(340, 'サマーゴースト', 'null', NULL, 'Tomoya, Aoi, and Ryou are high school students who met online. An urban legend speaks of a \"summer ghost,\" a spirit girl who appears when fireworks are set off.<br>\n<br>\nTomoya cannot live the life he envisioned for himself. Aoi cannot find her place in the world. Ryou has his once shining future suddenly pulled away. Each has their own reason for needing to meet the summer ghost. On a summer night when life and death cross paths, where will each of their emotions take them?', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":12,\"month\":11,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 50, 1, NULL, 1, 130050, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx130050-H9pyGqN3anh1.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(341, 'ARIA The BENEDIZIONE', 'null', NULL, 'The final part of the “Ao no Curtain Call” trilogy.', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":12,\"year\":2021}', 'NOT_YET_RELEASED', 7, 1, 60, 1, 130558, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx130558-8M8TeqrmQAbq.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(342, 'チキップダンサーズ', 'null', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 0, 1, 5, NULL, 130962, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx130962-cwoyKEGtIqY5.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(343, 'AMAIM Warrior at the Borderline', '境界戦機', NULL, 'In 2061 AD, Japan is dominated. Divided and ruled by the four major economic blocs of the world, the Japanese people spent their days oppressed as subjugated citizens. Japan became the front line of the world where AMAIM, a human-type special mobile weapon deployed by each economic zone, strode about.. One day, Amou Shiiba, a boy who loves machines, meets i-LeS (autonomous thinking AI) named \"Gai,\" and this leads him to throw himself into the battle to reclaim Japan, by piloting the AMAIM \"Kenbu\" built by himself.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 24, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 46, 1, 24, 25, 131005, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx131005-khLbX1nMCBxB.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(344, 'Irina: The Vampire Cosmonaut', '月とライカと吸血姫', NULL, 'Set in a fictional world, 10 years after a long war divided the world into two superpowers: the Union of Zirnitra Republics in the east, and the United Kingdom of Arnak in the west. Both of these superpowers now test their ambitions against each other in a space race. In 1960, the Union\'s Premier Gergiev announces the Mechtat Program, a prestigious plan to launch manned missions into the final frontier. To this end, the Republic establishes the isolated city of Laika 44, where cosmonaut candidates compete for planned manned missions to space, and scientists develop the technology to make it happen, all in an environment of secrecy.\n<br><br>\nThe story centers on Lev Leps, a backup astronaut candidate, and his new companion, the vampire Irina Ruminescu. As part of a daring new Operation Nosferatu, the Mechtat Program will use Irina as a test subject for various conditions expected in space, and ultimately as part of a manned mission, with Lev overseeing Irina\'s training as a cosmonaut. For reasons of their own, both dream of going into space.<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 36, 1, 'ノスフェラトゥ, The Moon, Laika, and Nosferatu, จันทรากับไลคร่าและเจ้าหญิงแวมไพร์, จันทรากับไลก้าและนอสเฟราตู', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 227, 1, 24, 12, 131019, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx131019-xaTtBN2G6BrO.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(345, 'Mieruko-chan', '見える子ちゃん', NULL, 'She can see dead people…she just chooses to ignore them. That’s Miko’s plan, anyway, but it doesn’t seem to be working for her in this love letter to the horror genre that will send shivers down your spine—and occasionally tickle your funny bone.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 117, 1, 'มิเอรุโกะจัง ใครว่าหนูเห็นผี', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 849, 1, 24, 12, 131083, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/131083-MYE8c1cuzO6C.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(346, 'Yashahime: Princess Half-Demon - The Second Act', '半妖の夜叉姫 弐の章', NULL, 'The second season of <i>Hanyou no Yashahime</i>.', 3, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 83, 1, 24, NULL, 131264, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/131264-2ZQFRto689Il.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(347, 'takt op.Destiny', 'takt op.Destiny', NULL, 'Music is the light that illuminates people\'s hearts-- and that \"light\" was suddenly taken from the world. The world changed the night the black \"Kuroya Meteorite\" fell. Grotesque monsters known as D2 emerged from the meteorite and began to overrun the land and people. As the D2 were drawn to melodies people played, eventually \"music\" itself became taboo. \n<br><br>\nHowever, those who opposed the monsters appeared. They the \"Musicart,\" girls who draw power from music. They possess the great operas and musical scores of humanity history and use them to defeat the D2.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 37, 1, 'タクトオーパス, แท็กต์ โอปัส. เดสตินี ~ลิขิตเสียง บรรเลงชะตา~', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 1183, 1, 24, NULL, 131565, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/131565-JBlm0IItFlUV.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(348, '呪術廻戦 0', 'null', NULL, 'Yuta Okkotsu is a nervous high school student who is suffering from a serious problem—his childhood friend Rika has turned into a curse and won\'t leave him alone. Since Rika is no ordinary curse, his plight is noticed by Satoru Gojo, a teacher at Jujutsu High, a school where fledgling exorcists learn how to combat curses. Gojo convinces Yuta to enroll, but can he learn enough in time to confront the curse that haunts him?\n<br><br>\n(Source: Viz Media)', 4, 1, 'JJK 0, 咒术回战0, มหาเวทย์ผนึกมาร 0', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":24,\"month\":12,\"year\":2021}', 'NOT_YET_RELEASED', 1018, 1, NULL, 1, 131573, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/131573-3veuVz5p0z2I.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(349, 'VISUAL PRISON', 'ヴィジュアルプリズン', NULL, 'Beautiful immortals have gathered in Harajuku to compete for a grand prize: Immense power! For years now the artists behind worldly culture and music have secretly been vampires, including those who produce Visual Kei. Now, they perform their most beautiful songs in the hallowed grounds of the Prison under the Scarlet Moon.<br><br>(Source: Funimation)', 3, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":10,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 142, 1, 24, 12, 131584, '2021-11-30 11:11:25', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/131584-oAAFNNZvQAqO.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo');
