(391, 'The Heike Story', '平家物語', NULL, 'A young orphan named Biwa is taken in by the powerful Taira Clan—also known as the Heike—after their leader witnesses her extraordinary psychic abilities. Unfortunately, what she predicts is a future of bloodshed, violence, and civil war. Inspired by the 12th-century epic tale Heike Monogatari.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 9, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2021, '{\"day\":16,\"month\":9,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 170, 1, 23, 11, 138714, '2021-11-30 11:11:27', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/138714-XnVrQIlHvu9J.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
