(468, 'VLAD LOVE', 'ぶらどらぶ', NULL, 'Mitsugu Bamba is a high school girl who is crazy about donating her blood, to the point that she feels compelled to visit a local blood bank despite the unfriendly nurse. One day, Mitsugu encounters a beautiful girl there who looks like she has come from overseas. The girl is so pale that she appears ready to faint. Instead, she suddenly starts trashing the blood bank. The girl then loses consciousness and so Mitsugu takes her home...<br><br>(Source: Official Website)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: The first episode was streamed on the official Vlad Love YouTube channel on Dec 18, 2020. The first 6 episodes were released on streaming platforms on Feb 14, 2021. The last 6 episodes were released on Mar 14, 2021.</i>', 1, 1, 'VLADLOVE', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":14,\"month\":2,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 82, 1, 24, 12, 110200, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/110200-w9PiOKLQm0z9.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(469, 'Attack on Titan Final Season', '進撃の巨人 The Final Season', NULL, 'It’s been four years since the Scout Regiment reached the shoreline, and the world looks different now. Things are heating up as the fate of the Scout Regiment—and the people of Paradis—are determined at last. However, Eren is missing. Will he reappear before age-old tensions between Marleyans and Eldians result in the war of all wars?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 11, 1, '[\"SnK 4\",\"AoT 4\",\"Shingeki no Kyojin 4\",\"\\u9032\\u6483\\u306e\\u5de8\\u4eba4\",\"Attack on Titan Season 4\",\"\\uc9c4\\uaca9\\uc758 \\uac70\\uc778 \\ub354 \\ud30c\\uc774\\ub110 \\uc2dc\\uc98c\",\"\\u05de\\u05ea\\u05e7\\u05e4\\u05ea \\u05d4\\u05d8\\u05d9\\u05d8\\u05d0\\u05e0\\u05d9\\u05dd \\u05d4\\u05e2\\u05d5\\u05e0\\u05d4 \\u05d4\\u05d0\\u05d7\\u05e8\\u05d5\\u05e0\\u05d4\",\"L\'Attaque des Titans Saison Finale\",\"L\'Attacco dei Giganti 4\",\"L\'Attacco dei Giganti - La Stagione Finale\",\" \\u0e1c\\u0e48\\u0e32\\u0e1e\\u0e34\\u0e20\\u0e1e\\u0e44\\u0e17\\u0e17', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":12,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 21498, 1, 24, 16, 110277, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/110277-iuGn6F5bK1U1.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(470, 'Bottom-Tier Character Tomozaki', '弱キャラ友崎くん', NULL, 'Expert gamer Tomozaki Fumiya doesn’t exactly fit in, but he wishes he did. With no written rules for success and gameplay that doesn’t work in his favor, the real world seems impossible for someone like him. But, like any noob, all he really needs are some strategies and a seasoned player like Aoi Hinami to help him. Hopefully with her guidance, Tomozaki will gain the experience he needs.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 2, 1, 'เกมพลิกโฉมนายกระจอก', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1073, 1, 24, 12, 112443, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/112443-w44XlUOHN5kh.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(471, 'Suppose a Kid from the Last Dungeon Boonies moved to a starter town?', 'たとえばラストダンジョン前の村の少年が序盤の街で暮らすような物語', NULL, 'The story follows Lloyd, a budding adventurer who just wants to get stronger. His plan? Head to the capital and discover his true power, even though he grew up being considered a weakling. So Lloyd heads out from his hometown, which interestingly exists directly next to the most dangerous dungeon. He might not think of himself as strong, but he’ll soon learn that there’s even more of a difference between him and other starting adventurers.<br>\n<br>\nYou know, because he grew up next to a deadly dungeon. He’s much stronger than he realizes.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 0, 1, 'LASDAN, Imagine, un cambrousard du dernier donjon dans la ville de départ !', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 688, 1, 24, 12, 112649, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/112649-jonCCVLHopXa.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(472, '2.43: Seiin High School Boys Volleyball Team', '2.43 清陰高校男子バレー部', NULL, 'High school student Kimichika Haijima moves back to his hometown, Fukui, after causing trouble in the Tokyo Junior High School volleyball club. There, he is reunited with his childhood friend, Yunii Kuroba, who possesses outstanding physical abilities, but is vulnerable under pressure. Haijima, with his overwhelming passion and talent for volleyball, forms an ace combination with Kuroba.<br><br>\n\nThe two enroll at Seiin High School, where they join the volleyball club. Awaiting them are the 163 cm hot-blooded captain Shinichirou Oda, the talented and sharp-tongued vice-captain Misao Aoki and his third-year pair, and second-year students, including Akito Kanno, who is always wearing long sleeves due to his allergy to sunlight.<br><br>\n\nThe newborn team breaks its former shell of weakness and becomes Fukui\'s rising star. This is a certain team\'s journey to victory, with a series of fascinating rivals standing in their way.\n', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 336, 1, 23, 12, 113231, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113231-QMe3Jv2BUqrb.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(473, 'Redo of Healer', '回復術士のやり直し', NULL, 'In a dark world of monsters, adventurers and mages, some of the most gifted healers are subjugated to brute force even by the hands of their compatriots. But one mage, Keyaru, gains the ability to rewind time, turn the tables and right all wrongs.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: This anime was aired at three broadcast censorship levels: a TV version, a streaming-exclusive \"Redo\" version, and an uncensored \"Complete Healing\" version, also translated as \"Complete Recovery,\" shown on AT-X.</i>', 2, 1, '回复术士的重启人生', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1992, 1, 24, 12, 113425, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113425-hcwuSZsuYMtt.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(474, 'Show by Rock!! Stars!!', 'SHOW BY ROCK!!STARS!!', NULL, 'The fourth season of <i>SHOW BY ROCK!!</i>.', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 52, 1, 24, 12, 113476, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113476-L368YN6wqSR1.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(475, 'Skate-Leading Stars', 'スケートリーディング☆スターズ', NULL, 'Kensei Maeshima left the world of figure skating after his rival said, “You’ll never beat me.” Years later, he’s using his athleticism to help several high school teams, never focusing on one. But when his adversary publicly announces a shift to a team sport, a kid familiar with Kensei’s past finds and offers him an invitation to lace up his skates and join the world of skate-leading.<br><br>(Source: Funimation)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: The series premiered on Funimation and affiliated streaming services (Wakanim, AnimeLab) on December 27, 2020. The Japanese broadcast started two weeks later on January 10, 2021.</i>', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":27,\"month\":12,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 137, 1, 24, 12, 113585, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113585-r4EAWR2igLml.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(476, 'planetarian ～雪圏球（スノーグローブ）', 'null', NULL, 'A New Planetarian OVA featuring the prequel short story \"Snow Globe,\" which debuted as part of a novel volume that bundled with a limited-edition version of the original PC game. <br><br>(Source: Anime News Network)<br><br>', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":20,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 23, 1, 37, 1, 113595, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx113595-2xZa6aoYq0ck.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(477, 'Seitokai Yakuindomo Movie 2', '劇場版 生徒会役員共２', NULL, 'The cast is back and ready to quip! In this companion film that follows season 2 of the zany, irreverent Seitokai Yakuindomo anime series, the student council must again grapple with a mix of double-entendres and doubly potent teen hormones.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: HIDIVE)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":1,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 60, 1, 80, 1, 113692, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx113692-N7hUICpi9sIa.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(478, 'Idoly Pride', 'IDOLY PRIDE', NULL, 'After a successful audition, high school student Kotono Nagase and her best friend move into a dorm with eight other aspiring idols. They quickly realize it takes more than cute choreography and cute outfits to reach the top—it will take blood, sweat, and tears to advance in the idol-ranking VENUS program, where the top spot is held by superstar Mana Nagase…who happens to be Kotono’s older sister.\n<br><br>(Source: Funimation)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 246, 1, 24, 12, 113814, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113814-X3M1HVWQHVIU.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(479, 'Dr. STONE: STONE WARS', 'Ｄｒ．ＳＴＯＮＥSTONE WARS', NULL, 'The second season of <i>Dr. STONE</i><br>\n<br>\nNow as he sets down blueprints for a smartphone in the stone world, Tsukasa and his Empire of Might prepare for the upcoming war. Who will be the victor in the fight for humanity?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 4, 1, 'ドクターストーン STONE WARS, Ｄｒ．ＳＴＯＮＥ第2期, Dr. STONE 2, 닥터 스톤 STONE WARS, 石纪元第二季', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":14,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 5048, 1, 24, 11, 113936, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113936-PpMtCY9kCwwV.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(480, 'Kemono Jihen', '怪物事変', NULL, 'Special detective Kohachi Inugami is sent to investigate a grisly phenomenon involving animal corpses near a remote mountain village. But after meeting a strange boy who agrees to help, he discovers cursed supernatural forces at work. Little by little, Inugami uncovers the truth behind the killings and the boy who may not even be human.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 3, 1, 'けものじへん, Monster Incidents, Kemono Incidents, คดีประหลาดคนปีศาจ', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1402, 1, 24, 12, 114085, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/114085-kIiJwfwnY1qL.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(481, 'World Trigger 2nd Season', 'ワールドトリガー 2ndシーズン', NULL, 'The second season of <i>World Trigger</i>.<br>\n<br>\nThe border defense organization \"Border\" was established to fight against the attacks of the \"Neighbors\" who possess unknown power. \nOsamu Mikumo, a member of the Border, forms the Mikumo Squad with Yuma Kuga, a Neighbor who he met by chance, and his childhood friend Chika Ametori, and they struggle to win the internal Border rankings in order to join the expeditionary force to the Neighborhood.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Toei Animation)', 2, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 448, 1, 23, 12, 114087, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx114087-5sSD98EFqQZ5.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(482, 'Gintama: THE VERY FINAL', '銀魂 THE FINAL', NULL, '<i>Gintama: THE FINAL</i> is the 3rd and final film adaptation of the remainder of the Silver Soul arc.', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1370, 1, 104, 1, 114129, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/114129-ZsLDkdwaYeJY.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(483, 'BEASTARS Season 2', 'BEASTARS 2', NULL, '\"Beastar\"—a title awarded to beasts who prove their excellence through fighting inequality to unite carnivores and herbivores in an anthropomorphic animal society. Cherryton Academy has gone five years without one such leader. However, following the murder of an alpaca within the school boundaries, the growing tension between the different species poses a greater need for a Beastar to ensure peace and harmony.<br>\n<br>\nWhen Louis, the prime candidate for this prestigious role, rejects the offer and leaves the academy, the student council declares to honor any student who captures the culprit of the aforementioned murder as Beastar. Meanwhile, Legoshi\'s sense of duty as a strong wolf who must protect the weak pushes him to investigate the incident. To further complicate his life, he struggles to manage his complex feelings for the white rabbit, Haru.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: The first episode had an early delivery on Netflix Japan on January 5, 2021. The regular TV broadcast started on January 7, 2021.</i>', 5, 1, 'BEASTARS 2nd Season', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1632, 1, 23, 12, 114194, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/114194-oYdHb4LhmHrs.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(484, 'Hortensia SAGA', 'オルタンシア・サーガ', NULL, 'When the duke of Hortensia murdered the king, he unleashed a wave of chaos that spilled the blood of many. Brazenly building his kingdom on the ashes of the old one, his violent rule has left many orphans in its wake. But now, the king’s heir has come of age. Living in secret as a man, she’s remained safe, and the time has come to gather allies to take back what is her’s—both country and throne!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 105, 1, 24, 12, 114301, '2021-11-30 11:16:14', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/114301-vPL85yxiKDTH.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(485, 'True Cooking Master Boy Season 2', '真・中華一番! 2', NULL, 'The second season of <i>Shin Chuuka Ichiban!</i>', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":12,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 6, 1, 24, 12, 114304, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/114304-cfF77duKvJNU.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(486, 'BACK ARROW', 'バック・アロウ', NULL, 'Lingalind is enclosed by the Wall. The Wall covers, protects, cultivates, and nurtures the land. The Wall is God. One day in Edger, a village on the outskirts, a mysterious man named Back Arrow appears. Arrow has no memory, but he claims that all he knows is that “I came from outside the Wall.” Arrow tries to go beyond the Wall to regain his memories but is pulled into one conflict after another.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 89, 1, 24, 24, 114307, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/114307-xmy1dyKDR7gE.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(487, 'AzurLane: Slow Ahead!', 'アズールレーンびそくぜんしんっ！', NULL, 'This is a slightly peculiar world where the shipgirls live in. A lively and enjoyable school life for girls from different factions will begin at the naval port of Azur Lane. Living out their lives to the fullest, these girls get into various shenanigans—slowly but surely!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, 'Azur Lane: Very Slow Advance!, Azur Lane 4-koma: Slow Ahead!, Anime AzurLane: Slow Ahead!, Azur Lane: Slow Ahead!', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":12,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 156, 1, 9, 12, 114473, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx114473-vnLrwMEZ9OfI.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(488, 'Log Horizon: Destruction of the Round Table', 'ログ・ホライズン　円卓崩壊', NULL, 'The third season of <i>Log Horizon</i>.<br>\n<br>\nIt’s been a year since Shiroe and his friends were trapped in Akiba due to the Catastrophe. Their forging of the Round Table has brought order and prosperity to its people. But fracturing political alliances and the constant menace of the Genius monsters threaten to destabilize all they’ve fought for and built. Can faith be restored and they persevere, or is its destruction truly inevitable?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 1, 1, 'Log Horizon 3', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 489, 1, 25, 12, 114862, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/114862-tM16kKlbGNMg.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(489, '囀る鳥は羽ばたかない Don\'t stay gold ', 'null', NULL, 'The anime is based on a short story Yoneda wrote about Kageyama and Kuga\'s first meeting. The OVA will ship with a special edition of the seventh volume of the original manga.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Saezuru Tori wa Habatakanai OVA, Twittering Birds Never Fly OVA , Don\'t Stay Gold', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":1,\"month\":3,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 37, 1, 24, 1, 115567, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/115567-8hMWE9NCRS0e.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(490, 'Tokyo 7th シスターズ -僕らは青空になる-', 'null', NULL, 'Donuts\' Tokyo 7th Sisters smartphone game celebrated its sixth anniversary by announcing a brand-new 70-minute anime adaptation by Toei Animation. Theaters will screen the new anime for a limited \"simultaneous\" run this summer. The teaser video for the game\'s sixth anniversary ends with the tagline, \"The summer of Tokyo 7th Sisters is coming again.\"<br><br>(Source: Anime News Network, edited)\n', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":26,\"month\":2,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 11, 1, 86, 1, 116069, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx116069-W773lKgeElXP.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(491, 'Otherside Picnic', '裏世界ピクニック', NULL, 'Moments from death, Sorawo is saved by the mysterious Toriko in the Otherside. Attracted to its beauty, she soon discovers that this dimension is inhabited by monsters once thought imaginary. Joining with Toriko in her search for a missing friend, they set out to explore this nightmare-realm and maybe make a little money. What they encounter could bring enlightenment—or drive them mad!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 1, 1, 'Urasekai Picnic, ฝ่าปริศนาตะลุยโลกเบื้องหลัง', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 300, 1, 24, 12, 116287, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/116287-3cIsgAy5bIuC.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(492, 'The Seven Deadly Sins: Dragon\'s Judgement', '七つの大罪 憤怒の審判', NULL, 'Time is running out. The curse imposed on Elizabeth will kill her in few days. To lift the curse Meliodas and Ban have travelled to the Demon Realm to challenge Meliodas\' father, the Demon King.\n<br><br>\nMeanwhile, Merlin, Escanor, and Archangel Ludociel are set to slay Meliodas\' brother Zeldris. Elsewhere, Meliodas\' other brother Estarossa has kidnapped Elizabeth, and it falls to King, Diane, Gowther, and Hawk to rescue her.', 4, 1, '七大罪：愤怒的审判, The Seven Deadly Sins: Dragens dom, ศึกตำนาน 7 อัศวิน ภาค 4', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1441, 1, 24, 24, 116752, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/116752-P72hkhtqD76t.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(493, 'WIXOSS DIVA(A)LIVE', 'WIXOSS DIVA(A)LIVE', NULL, 'The story moves the \"Wixoss\" card game to the online virtual space of \"Wixossland\" as it continues to grow more popular. The game allows players to become the LRIG avatars themselves. The most popular format in the game is \"Diva Battle,\" which allows three players to team up to compete against other units for the most \"Selector\" fans. Some units are idol-themed, while others are DJ- and band-themed.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 32, 1, 24, 12, 116944, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/116944-19LDc8fsTqsc.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(494, 'Kiyo in Kyoto: From the Maiko House', '舞妓さんちのまかないさん', NULL, 'Kiyo and Sumire came to Kyoto from Aomori Prefecture, dreaming of becoming maiko. But after an unexpected turn of events, Kiyo starts working as the live-in cook at the Maiko House. Their story unfolds in Kagai, the Geiko and maiko district in Kyoto, alongside their housemate maikos. Kiyo nourishes them daily with her homecooked meals, and Sumire strives toward her promising future as the once-in-a-century maiko.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: Each episode is released on the fourth Thursday of each month. One episode usually features three chapters.</i>', 0, 1, 'The caterer at the Maiko Manor', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":25,\"month\":2,\"year\":2021}', 'RELEASING', 36, 1, 25, 12, 117067, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/117067-6Wk2OduSnKxK.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(495, 'Sorcerous Stabber Orphen: Battle of Kimluck', '魔術士オーフェンはぐれ旅 キムラック編', NULL, 'The second season of <i>Majutsushi Orphen Hagure Tabi</i>.<br>\n<br>\nOrphen now knows Azalie\'s true motive and heads to the holy city of Kimluck. However, a fierce battle with the \"Death Teacher\" awaits him.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 0, 1, 'Majutsushi Orphen Hagure Tabi 2', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":20,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 42, 1, 24, 11, 117085, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/117085-xCc4jwzyKHAe.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(496, 'Cells at Work! CODE BLACK', 'はたらく細胞BLACK', NULL, 'A rookie Red Blood Cell has been bustling about, frantically making oxygen deliveries all around the body! But his workplace is on the brink of going Code Black!! Drinking, smoking, stress, sleep deprivation... Struggling to survive a life not unlike the brutal corporate world, what must these overworked cells be thinking at the end of the day? This is a tale about the inside of your body...<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)<br>\n<br>\n<i>Notes:<br>\n- The episodes were streamed two days ahead of the Japanese broadcast on Funimation beginning on Jan 8, 2021 at 2:30 JST. The regular TV broadcast started on Jan 10, 2021 at 0:00 JST.</i><br>\n<i>- Episodes 3 and 4 were broadcast in Japan as a one hour special episode on Jan 19, 2021 at 1:40 JST.</i>', 2, 1, 'Les brigades immunitaires BLACK', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 422, 1, 24, 13, 117533, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/117533-QncrEV8PjWUc.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(497, 'ARIA The CREPUSCOLO', 'null', NULL, 'The season is fall and the city of Neo-Venezia is covered in fallen leaves. Something is bothering Anya, who works at Orange Planet. Her senior colleagues Alice and Athena haven’t seen each other due to their busy schedules, which is making Athena feel sad. But for some reason, Alice seems to be avoiding her altogether. With her friends Ai and Azusa’s help, Anya tries to find a definitive way for Alice and Athena to get together. But during this time, Anya learns of a situation that only she can see because of where she stands.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Shochiku Films)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":3,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 41, 1, 60, 1, 117556, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/117556-VUxI7HA5hJ9G.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(498, 'Heaven’s Design Team', '天地創造デザイン部', NULL, 'I made the light, the water, and the earth below. Now it\'s time to make the life that dwells upon it. Actually... that sounds like a giant headache, so I\'ll contract it out! Heaven\'s Design Team is an agency that creates made-to-order life forms for their client, God. Why does this life form look like that? Why does this life form live this way? Watch the trials and successes of the designers and engineers forced to breathe life into God\'s absurd requests!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, 'Tendebu', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 210, 1, 24, 12, 117696, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/117696-VdaMljYfJT0h.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(499, 'The Hidden Dungeon Only I Can Enter', '俺だけ入れる隠しダンジョン', NULL, 'The Hidden Dungeon is a place of legend where rare treasures and items are hidden. Noir, the third son of an impoverished noble family who\'s lost the one job offer he had, was lucky enough to hear about this dungeon. He then acquires a skill that allows him to create, bestow, and edit skills... and in order to use it, he needs to accumulate points by carrying out such tasks as eating delicious meals and doing sexual things with alluring members of the opposite sex.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 2, 1, 'Special training in the Secret Dungeon!', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 1036, 1, 24, 12, 118375, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/118375-R4y2nIid48Uw.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(500, 'LBX Girls', '装甲娘戦機', NULL, 'In an unplanned field trip, Riko is transported to an alternate Japan where metal-based life forms known as Mimesis ravage the world. Only girls equipped with LBX armored weaponry can stand up to this scourge. Joined by four other displaced young women, Riko will have to adapt to save humanity. The hope of a planet now rests on these heavy metal soldiers who desire one wish—to return home again!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 27, 1, 24, 12, 119123, '2021-11-30 11:16:15', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx119123-KmxEMsv7q0uR.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(501, 'Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World- Season 2 Part 2', 'Re:ゼロから始める異世界生活 2nd Season Part 2', NULL, 'After learning more behind the Death Loop and Witches of Sin, Subaru vows to save Emilia and his friends from further doom.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 5, 1, 'Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu (2021), Re: 제로부터 시작하는 이세계 생활 2기 파트 2, Re:从零开始的异世界生活第二季（下半）, Re:从零开始的异世界生活 2 下半', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 5883, 1, 30, 12, 119661, '2021-11-30 11:16:16', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/119661-9C7DvtL7yfCu.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(502, 'Bungo Stray Dogs WAN!', '文豪ストレイドッグス わん！', NULL, 'The peaceful days of the very popular work Bungou Stray Dogs are here. The characters of the Armed Detective Agency and the Mafia are in miniature form?! Due to Atsushi and co. becoming cute, this is a different experience to the original work.', 3, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 686, 1, 12, 12, 120150, '2021-11-30 11:16:16', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/120150-bkyCLDwgKG88.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(503, 'World Witches Take Off!', 'ワールドウィッチーズ発進しますっ！', NULL, NULL, 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 22, 1, 14, 12, 121681, '2021-11-30 11:16:16', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx121681-yQBcravTSQhy.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(505, 'Oh, Suddenly Egyptian God', 'とーとつにエジプト神', NULL, 'Welcome to the world of the Egyptian gods.<br>\n<br>\nThis is where the famous gods of Ancient Egypt, from Anubis to Thoth, live their lives freely.<br>\n<br>\nHow freely, you ask? Bastet appears out of nowhere, singing and dancing. Medjed is always stone-faced. Horus works a part-time job. Set is devoted to pulling pranks. Ra\'s off traveling and rarely comes home... All the Gods basically just do whatever they want!<br><br>(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, 'Suddenly, Egyptian Gods', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":12,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 21, 1, 5, 10, 123474, '2021-11-30 11:16:16', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx123474-goJkeXu38bhV.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(506, 'Dr. Ramune -Mysterious Disease Specialist-', '怪病医ラムネ', NULL, 'As long as hearts exist inside people, there will always be those who suffer. And then something \"strange\" enters their mind and causes a strange disease to manifest itself in the body. The illness, which is called a \"mystery disease\" is unknown to most, but certainly exists. There is a doctor and apprentice who fights the disease, which modern medicine cannot cure.<br>\n <br>\nHis name is Ramune.<br>\n <br>\nHe acts freely all the time, is foul-mouthed, and doesn’t even look like a doctor! However, once he is confronted with the mysterious disease, he is able to quickly uncover the root cause of his patients\' deep-seated distress and cure them.<br>\n <br>\nAnd beyond that...<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 2, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 225, 1, 24, 12, 123779, '2021-11-30 11:16:16', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/123779-Ck1nQb0mZ8zJ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(507, 'Scar on the Praeter', 'プレイタの傷', NULL, 'After a rebellion in the Akatsuki Special Ward of Tokyo, the government collapses and citizens are left to fend for themselves. With Divine Tattoos that each possess unique powers, agents known as the Scard rise up to become the protectors of peace.\n\nBut loyal to three contending organizations, they’ll have to face more than just criminals in order to serve their own definitions of justice.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 0, 1, 'PROJECT SCARD: Praeter no Kizu', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 81, 1, 24, 13, 123785, '2021-11-30 11:16:16', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/123785-RPyFqAw3o3Nx.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(508, 'Horimiya', 'ホリミヤ', NULL, 'A secret life is the one thing they have in common. At school, Hori is a prim and perfect social butterfly, but the truth is she\'s a brash homebody. Meanwhile, under a gloomy facade, Miyamura hides a gentle heart, along with piercings and tattoos. In a chance meeting, they both reveal a side they\'ve never shown. Could this blossom into something new?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 10, 1, '堀与宫村, โฮริมิยะ สาวมั่นกับนายมืดมน', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 14283, 1, 24, 13, 124080, '2021-11-30 11:16:16', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/124080-ARyLAHHgikRq.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(509, 'Gekidol', 'ゲキドル', NULL, 'Five years after a mystifying disaster decimates cities across the globe, Seria Morino receives an invitation from a mysterious woman to join Alice in Theater, a small stage troupe that takes it upon themselves to brighten the world through their performances using 3D hologram technology. As Seria settles in, she begins to uncover unexpected truths about herself and the world around her…<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)<br><br>\n<i>Note: The BD box with all episodes was released on Mar 3, 2021. The regular broadcast ended on Mar 23, 2021 on AT-X.</i>', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 42, 1, 23, 12, 124131, '2021-11-30 11:16:16', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/124131-kcN3OgjqFS7d.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(510, '夏目友人帳 石起こしと怪しき来訪者', 'null', NULL, 'In \"Ishi Okoshi,\" Natsume meets a small youkai called Mitsumi in a forest. Mitsumi is entrusted to wake up the divine youkai \"Iwatetsu\" from its deep slumber. Mitsumi weighs on Natsume\'s mind, so he sets out to help Mitsumi with his task.\n<br><br>\nIn \"Ayashiki Raihousha,\" a mysterious visitor appears in front of Tanuma. Nearly every day, the visitor visits Tanuma, talks to him a little, and then leaves. Natsume, who knows the visitor is a youkai, worries for Tanuma, but Tanuma enjoys these exchanges with the youkai. The youkai means no harm, but Tanuma\'s health slowly starts to deteriorate.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Natsume\'s Book of Friends: The Waking Rock and the Strange Visitor', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":16,\"month\":1,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 59, 1, 51, 1, 124132, '2021-11-30 11:16:16', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx124132-1CMeg6ZKv09Q.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
