(570, 'DELIVER POLICE/西東京市デリバー警察隊', 'null', NULL, 'In the near future, transportation has developed. The Japanese government, feeling that the conventional police were limited in their power of maintaining security, decided to allow citizens to assist with arresting criminals with the limitation of being limited to the designated area. This was the birth of the Deliver Police. The main character, Taichi, has dreamt of being a hero since he was a child, is active as one of those Delivery Police, in addition to his main job of making anime. Can he and operator Kazuko arrest the villains in time?<br>\n<br>\n<i>Note: One of the four short movies that showed in Animenotane 2021.</i>', 0, 1, 'Anime no Tane 2021', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2021, '{\"day\":26,\"month\":3,\"year\":2021}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 10, 1, 136139, '2021-11-30 11:16:17', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b136139-QAZWqbl1IMod.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
