(695, 'レベッカ', 'null', NULL, 'Rebecca is a 10-year-old cheerful and energetic girl who is the second of seven children. She lives in a rural town in Maine in the United States at the end of the 19th century. After her father dies, her family descends into poverty, and Rebecca unwillingly goes to live with her aunts Miranda and Jane. Rebecca loves her kind aunt Jane dearly, but her aunt Miranda is naggy and strict.<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)<br><br><i>The movie was planned to be screened on March 14, but the event was cancelled due to concerns of COVID-19 spread.</i>', 0, 1, 'Young Animator Training Project 2020, Anime Tamago 2020, The Chronicles of Rebecca', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2020, '{\"day\":27,\"month\":3,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 2, 1, 24, 1, 114945, '2021-11-30 11:17:08', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx114945-YimcesTfneqf.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(696, 'みちるレスキュー！', 'null', NULL, 'Four glowing orbs of different color fly through space, chasing after a dark red orb. After a fierce battle, only the blue orb falls to earth, into the room where Michiru is sleeping. But the dark red orb also appears on earth. The orb changes shape into the form of a boy, and starts to illegally raise Mejiro birds. Later, Michiru is at a flea market in a park, when a large flock of Mejiro birds cover the sky, and start attacking people. The yellow, silver, and purple orbs show up and almost manage to calm down the Mejiro, but violence is about to break out again. At that moment, Michiru hears a voice inside her head asking her to save the Mejiro.<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)<br><br><i>The movie was planned to be screened on March 14, but the event was cancelled due to concerns of COVID-19 spread.</i>', 0, 1, 'Young Animator Training Project 2020, Anime Tamago 2020', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2020, '{\"day\":27,\"month\":3,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 1, 1, NULL, 1, 114946, '2021-11-30 11:17:08', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx114946-muGFJUwuiKWV.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(698, 'オメテオトル≠HERO', 'null', NULL, 'In the year 22XX, due to the drastic decrease in the human population, the government starts accepting races from other allied planets. As a result of genetic mixing, new species are born with special powers. A young man named Yuuki learns on his 18th birthday that while his father is a member of the \"hero\" tribe, his mother is a member of a tribe of beings who can manipulate plants who were supposedly wiped out due to the accelerated mechanization of the planet. As a result, Yuuki holds powers of both tribes, but he questions which side he should help with his powers.<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)<br><br><i>The movie was planned to be screened on March 14, but the event was cancelled due to concerns of COVID-19 spread.</i>', 0, 1, 'Young Animator Training Project 2020, Anime Tamago 2020', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2020, '{\"day\":27,\"month\":3,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 1, 1, 24, 1, 114948, '2021-11-30 11:17:08', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b114948-zarZxhKxW2vP.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(700, 'DIGIMON ADVENTURE 20th memorial story', 'デジモンアドベンチャー20th メモリアルストーリー', NULL, 'A series of prequel anime shorts that will tell side stories not shown in <i>Digimon Adventure: Last Evolution Kizuna</i>.<br>\n<br>\nOver ten years have passed since that initial adventure. Sora worries over what she should do with her future. What choice has she ultimately arrived at?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Toei Animation)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2020, '{\"day\":1,\"month\":2,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 15, 1, 6, 5, 115107, '2021-11-30 11:17:08', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx115107-GUXZ5XoMfNYW.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
