(751, 'Poupelle of Chimney Town', 'えんとつ町のプぺル', NULL, 'The story is set in a town surrounded by a wall that stands 4,000 meters (about 2.5 miles) tall. Because the town is full of chimneys, the air is always full of smoke. No one in the town knows what the sky looks like. On one night of the town\'s Halloween festival, a deliveryman accidentally drops the heart he is supposed to deliver. He cannot find the heart in the smoke and gives up. The heart continues to beat where it fell in the town of chimneys.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2020, '{\"day\":25,\"month\":12,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 7, 1, 100, 1, 98776, '2021-11-30 11:17:56', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/98776-UECg5RN6qZlC.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(752, 'Strike Witches: Road to Berlin', '第501統合戦闘航空団 ストライクウィッチーズ ROAD to BERLIN', NULL, 'They’re back! And with Shizuka Hattori, a dutiful new member of the 501st Fighter Wing girls in tow, the Strike Witches have never been more ready to win the war on Neuroi once and for all.\n\nWill the girls prevail in the epic battle to reclaim Berlin, or is humanity doomed? Get ready for a battle that will knock your socks (or pants) right off! \n(Source: Funimation)', 0, 1, 'Strike Witches 3', 'japan', 'FALL', 2020, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":10,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 76, 1, 24, 12, 103119, '2021-11-30 11:17:56', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx103119-5x83l4nwlloI.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(753, 'Fate/Grand Order Divine Realm of the Round Table: Camelot - Wandering; Agateram', '劇場版 Fate/Grand Order -神聖円卓領域キャメロット- 前編 Wandering; Agateram', NULL, 'The wandering knight, Bedivere, reaches the end of his journey.\n<br><br>\nThe year is A.D. 1273 in Jerusalem.\n<br><br>\nThe Holy Land has been transformed into a massive desert, the people have been forced out of their homes, and three major powers wage war with each other in this wasteland. The Knights of the Round Table come together to protect the Holy City and their Lion King. With the whole of his kingdom summoned into a strange land, Ozymandias, the Sun-King, quietly plots against the tyranny of this bizarre realm.\n<br><br>\nThe mountain people, protectors of those who were stripped of their land, await their chance at rebellion. In order to fulfill his mission, Bedivere heads for the Holy City where the Lion King rules. There he meets humanity’s final Master, Ritsuka Fujimaru, who has come to Jerusalem, accompanied by his Demi-Servant, Mash Kyrielight, in their quest to restore human history.\n<br><br>\nBedivere joins with Fujimaru and his companions to undertake this quest.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Official Website) ', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'FALL', 2020, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":12,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 153, 1, 89, 1, 103276, '2021-11-30 11:17:56', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/103276-Al60Ha42yp1h.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(754, 'Is the Order a Rabbit? BLOOM', 'ご注文はうさぎですか？ BLOOM', NULL, 'The third season of <i>Gochuumon wa Usagi desu ka?</i><br>\n<br>\nAs summer turns to autumn, the colorful Rabbit House regulars return to serve up warm treats and tasty drinks at the Rabbit House café — along with a heaping helping of adorable antics and cute capers, of course!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: HIDIVE)', 0, 1, 'Gochiusa', 'japan', 'FALL', 2020, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":10,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 285, 1, 25, 12, 104198, '2021-11-30 11:17:56', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/104198-z44oIGYnR5Zf.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
