(915, 'Given The Movie', '映画 ギヴン', NULL, 'The film centers on the love relationship among the band\'s bassist Haruki Nakayama, drummer Akihiko Kaji, and Akihiko\'s roommate and ex-boyfriend Ugetsu Murata.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":22,\"month\":8,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 3022, 1, 60, 1, 111734, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/111734-e9qFEmADPAzs.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(916, 'デート・ア・バレット デッド・オア・バレット', 'null', NULL, 'The first part of <i>Date A Bullet</i>.\n<br><br>\nHibiki Higoromo, better known as, Empty, is an amnesiac young girl. She wakes up in the neighboring world, where she encounters Tokisaki Kurumi. In order to kill the mysterious girl, Kurumi leads Empty to a school. When arriving at the school, a number of girls, known as semi-spirits, gather together. Now then, a new battle begins.<br><br>(Source: Wikipedia)', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":14,\"month\":8,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 307, 1, 25, 1, 111852, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx111852-W3cRNx9CO7sJ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(917, 'Peter Grill and the Philosopher\'s Time', 'ピーターグリルと賢者の時間', NULL, 'Peter Grill is the world’s strongest fighter, but his ascent to the top came with an unexpected consequence: Women around the world, human and monster alike, want to bear his genetically superior children! Since he’s currently engaged to the love of his life, Peter isn’t too keen on his sudden popularity, and it will take every ounce of self-control for Peter to keep his hands to himself and his relationship with his paramour in one piece!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":11,\"month\":7,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 343, 1, 12, 12, 111965, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/111965-i9aeO9gvuH8e.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(918, '超普通都市カシワ伝説R', 'null', NULL, 'A surreal gag anime about female junior high school students who along with mysterious creatures attend a junior high school set in the real Kashiwa town, together loosely conveying the charm of Kashiwa with contents related to the town and its events.', 0, 1, 'The Legend of Super Normal City Kashiwa R', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":7,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 5, 1, 5, 10, 112258, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx112258-euCskvIy0fix.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(919, 'The Misfit of Demon King Academy: History’s Strongest Demon King Reincarnates and Goes to School with His Descendants', '魔王学院の不適合者 ～史上最強の魔王の始祖、転生して子孫たちの学校へ通う～', NULL, 'Anos, the Demon King of Tyranny, has defeated humans, spirits, and gods alike. But even demon kings get tired of all the fighting sometimes! Hoping for a more peaceful life, Anos decides to reincarnate himself. When he wakes two thousand years later, though, he finds the world has become too peaceful--his descendants have grown weak and magic is in serious decline. Intending to reclaim his rightful place, he enrolls in Demon King Academy, where he finds that his magical power is off the charts. Literally. And because they can\'t measure his power, the faculty and other students regard Anos as a misfit. With the support of Misha, the one student he manages to befriend, the misfit (Demon King) begins his climb up the demon ranks!\n<br><br>\n(Source: Square Enix Manga & Books)', 3, 1, 'Maou Gakuin no Futekigousha, The Misfit of Demon King Academy, 魔王学院の不適合者, ใครว่าข้าไม่เหมาะเป็นจอมมาร', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":7,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 3693, 1, 24, 13, 112301, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/112301-e50SRjhGDGUu.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(920, 'Japan Sinks: 2020', '日本沈没2020', NULL, 'The setting for this adaptation is moved from 1970s Japan to 2020, just after the Tokyo Olympics. The story centers on the Mutou family, and the siblings Ayumu and Gou. The four members of the Mutou family are caught in an earthquake that hits Tokyo, and attempt to escape the city, while disaster claws at their heels.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 1, 1, '2020: Japão Submerso, El Hundimiento de Japón: 2020, Japón se hunde: 2020', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":7,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 436, 1, 25, 10, 112357, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/112357-EYHpCNuYJXlZ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(921, 'The Stranger by the Shore', '海辺のエトランゼ', NULL, 'After coming out to his parents, aspiring novelist Shun Hashimoto has no one to turn to, until the day he meets high schooler Mio Chibana on the beach. The two instantly click—just before Mio has to leave for the mainland. Now three years later, Mio returns with a confession. But after all this time, will Shun feel the same?<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 2, 1, 'Seaside Stranger, Umibe no Etranger, L\'Étranger de la plage, The Stranger by the Beach', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":11,\"month\":9,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 1855, 1, 59, 1, 112788, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/112788-stKeBgPcY7l2.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(922, 'No Guns Life Season 2', 'ノー・ガンズ・ライフ 第2期', NULL, 'Juuzo Inui’s next mission is to rescue Rosa McMahon, a girl who holds a valuable piece of data the Berühren Corporation is after. Still reeling from Colt’s death, Tetsurou swears to never hesitate again.<br>\n<br>\nAnd somewhere in the city, Pepper is determined to make Juuzo her property along with her current Gun Slave Unit, Seven.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":7,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 135, 1, 24, 12, 112803, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/112803-nY631RWlndb0.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(923, 'SUPER HXEROS', 'ド級編隊エグゼロス', NULL, 'Earth faces an unprecedented threat from an invasion by the mysterious Kiseichuu. The Kiseichuu feed on human sexual energy, also known as “H-energy”, and weaken the human population.<br>\n<br>\nHigh school student Retto Enjou is a member of the hero group HXEROS, who fight together to save the earth from the Kiseichuu.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":7,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 303, 1, 24, 12, 112818, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/112818-l9jhlxOIv2kQ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(924, '少女☆歌劇 レヴュースタァライト ロンド・ロンド・ロンド', 'null', NULL, 'A compilation film recapping the anime series.', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":8,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 41, 1, 119, 1, 113023, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx113023-ppUSdBgb9pzc.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(925, 'Monster Girl Doctor', 'モンスター娘のお医者さん', NULL, 'Here in the town of Lindworm, where humans and monsters coexist, a new young doctor, Glenn, begins another day of perilous medical exams! Whether he\'s examining deep inside a mermaid\'s gills, stitching up a flesh golem\'s thigh, assisting a harpy in laying her eggs, or palpating every last scale on a dragon, Glenn is just doing his best to help these girls whose appearances and bodies are all so completely different... so why does he always end up in such precarious positions with his patients? It\'s all good, though, because it\'s strictly for medical purposes! He may come close to suffocating from the pressure of his lamia assistant Saphentite\'s tail coiling around him, but still, the clinic is open for business in this medical fantasy that explores the physiologies of monster girls as never before!<br><br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)<br><br>\n<i>The first episode premiered a week early on streaming services</i>', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":12,\"month\":7,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 451, 1, 24, 12, 113286, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx113286-AUS3PAJ5n6BU.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(926, 'Rent-a-Girlfriend', '彼女、お借りします', NULL, 'In today’s Japan, “rental” services can deliver an afternoon with a “friend,” a “parent,” even a fake girlfriend! After a staggering betrayal by his girlfriend, hapless freshman Kazuya gets just desperate enough to give it a try. But he quickly discovers how complicated it can be to “rent” an emotional connection, and his new “girlfriend,” who’s trying to keep her side hustle secret, will panic when she finds out her real life and Kazuya’s are intertwined in surprising ways! Family, school, and life all start to go wrong, too…\n<br><br>\n(Source: Kodansha USA)', 5, 1, 'I\'d like to Borrow a Girlfriend, Kanokari', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":11,\"month\":7,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 5159, 1, 24, 12, 113813, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/113813-Al8VofQuNQHV.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(927, 'ORESUKI: Are you the only one who loves me?: Our Playball / Our End Run / Our Game', '俺を好きなのはお前だけかよ～俺たちのゲームセット～', NULL, 'Hose is the ultimate romantic comedy protagonist, who is more talented and better than me at everything. Hose and I are going to battle over Pansy at the fateful regional tournament finals. While Nishikizuta and Toshobu high schools go head-to-head in a baseball match, I’m going to battle Hose in a popularity contest. Yes, I’m going to fight fair and square…Psych! Of course not! The odds are overwhelmingly against me, so I’m going to play dirty! Mwahahaha! I know that Hose is going to follow the rules to the tee, so I’m going to do the exact opposite…Huh? What did you say? There are some new rules? Wait a sec!<br>\n<br>\nWhy are all the rules in favor of the other guy? Himawari, Cosmos, Asunaro! Why did you betray me? Crap…I have no one on my side…The rules are all twisted…So, I have no shame in using all my dirty tricks so everyone can see!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":9,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 404, 1, 70, 1, 114195, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/114195-op9SJ1D86eNI.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(928, 'Fire Force Season 2', '炎炎ノ消防隊 弐ノ章', NULL, 'Shinra and Company 8 have figured out the Evangelist’s goal: to gather Adolla Bursts from Shinra and Shou. After learning more about his past from Captain Burns, Shinra becomes more motivated to discover the truth about his mother and save Shou again.<br>\n<br>\nBut a mysterious girl known as the “First Pillar” reveals the Evangelist’s master plan to start another Great Cataclysm!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Funimation)', 11, 1, 'Enen no Shouboutai 2, หน่วยผจญคนไฟลุก ภาค 2', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":7,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 3517, 1, 24, 24, 114236, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/114236-6nbw38bHeXYQ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(929, '22/7: 8＋3＝？', 'null', NULL, 'Extra thirteenth episode included in the sixth Blu-ray & DVD volume of <i>22/7</i>.<br><br>\n\n22/7 was revived for the fans on December 24th, which was their day of formation.The next day, when eight people came to the office, the Wall was completely revived, and the mystery only deepened. To dispel the disturbing feelings, Sakura proposes to have a Christmas party to celebrate the reunion.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Funimation)', 0, 1, '22/7 Episode 13, 22/7 OVA, Nanabun no Nijyuuni Episode 13', 'japan', 'SUMMER', 2020, '{\"day\":16,\"month\":9,\"year\":2020}', 'FINISHED', 15, 1, 24, 1, 114249, '2021-11-30 11:18:46', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/114249-IJJQl5ZZ09zJ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo');
