(1261, 'タナバタノオト', 'null', NULL, 'Nanase lives in a village where the stars are the most beautiful in Japan and when she hears the story of Orihime and Hikoboshi, she gazes up at the night sky every day and thinks about them. When Nanase moved to a new town, she was shocked to see the sky of the city. There are no stars in the night sky, which means that Orihime and Hikoboshi cannot meet! Nanase unconsciously writes in her notebook, \"How can I make the Milky Way?\"<br><br>\nThere were three girls who happened to find her scribbling in her notebook. Riko, the leader of the group and a strong person. Mio, who loves science. Airi is a sucker for anything trendy. This is the start of a reckless attempt to create the Milky Way by the four girls, who have very different interests and personalities.<br><br>\n(Source: Official Announcement, Translated)\n<br><br>\nShort animated music videos celebrating the 100th anniversary of Calpis, featuring songs from 5 different Japanese artists.<br><br>\n• \"Musubareta Omoi\" (結ばれた想い) by Shiritsu Ebisu Chuugaku<br>\n• \"Kimi to Mitai Keshiki\" (君と見たい景色) by MaRuRi & Ryuga<br>\n• \"Shoukei\" (憧景) by Oisicle Melonpan<br>\n• \"Ao\" (青) by KOBASOLO feat. harutya<br>\n• \"Sora ni Hikaru\" (空に光る) by Toy cleanse', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2019, '{\"day\":25,\"month\":6,\"year\":2019}', 'FINISHED', 2, 1, 2, 5, 140202, '2021-11-30 11:19:48', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/140202-qNCrlmCPuNaq.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1301, 'Legend of the Galactic Heroes: Die Neue These', '銀河英雄伝説 -Die Neue These- 邂逅', NULL, 'In humanity\'s distant future, two interstellar states—the monarchic Galactic Empire and the democratic Free Planets Alliance—are embroiled in a never-ending war. The story focuses on the exploits of rivals Reinhard von Müsel and Yang Wen Li as they rise to power and fame in the Galactic Empire and the Free Planets Alliance.<br>', 0, 1, 'Legend of the Galactic Heroes: The New Thesis - Encounter, La Leyenda de los Héroes de la Galaxia: La Nueva Tesis', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 227, 1, 25, 12, 20628, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/20628-74FNU1vibTHU.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1302, 'シュタインズ・ゲート ゼロ', 'null', NULL, 'The eccentric, self-proclaimed mad scientist Rintarou Okabe has become a shell of his former self. Depressed and traumatized after failing to rescue his friend, he has decided to forsake his mad scientist alter ego and live as an ordinary college student. Surrounded by friends who know little of his time travel experiences, Okabe spends his days trying to forget the horrors of his adventures alone.<br>\n<br>\nWhile working as a receptionist at a college technology forum, Okabe meets the short, spunky Maho Hiyajo, who\nlater turns out to be the interpreter at the forum\'s presentation, conducted by Professor Alexis Leskinen. In front of a stunned crowd, Alexis and Maho unveil Amadeus—a revolutionary AI capable of storing a person\'s memories and creating a perfect simulation of that person complete with their personality and quirks. Meeting with Maho and Alexis after the presentation, Okabe learns that the two were Kurisu\'s colleagues in university, and that they have simulated her in Amadeus. Hired by Alexis to research the simulation\'s behavior, Okabe is given the chance to interact with the shadow of a long-lost dear friend. Dangerously tangled in the past, Okabe must face the harsh reality and carefully maneuver around the disastrous consequences that come with disturbing the natural flow of time.\n', 0, 1, 's;g0, 命运石之门0', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":12,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 4414, 1, 24, 23, 21127, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21127-6jTjz7ndTHOi.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1303, 'Full Metal Panic! Invisible Victory', 'フルメタル・パニック！Invisible Victory', NULL, 'Nine months have passed since teen soldier Sousuke Sagara first became Kaname Chidori\'s covert protector. In that time, Mithril has been remarkably successful at thwarting Amalgam\'s efforts, but this has only made Amalgam more determined. Leonard Testarossa\'s visits with Tessa and Kaname are just preludes to all-out attacks that begin with global communications disruptions. Kaname\'s status as a Whispered makes her one of Amalgam\'s main targets, which means that any semblance of a peaceful life at Jindai Municipal High School is now over for her.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'FULL METAL PANIC! IV', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 170, 1, 24, 12, 21451, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21451-n724W1YmcdPZ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1304, 'FLCL Progressive', 'フリクリ プログレ', NULL, 'Many years have passed since Naota and Haruhara Haruko shared their adventure together. Meanwhile, the war between the two entities known as Medical Mechanica and Fraternity rages across the galaxy. Enter Hidomi, a young teenaged girl who believes there is nothing amazing to expect from her average life, until one day when a new teacher named Haruko arrives at her school. Soon enough, Medical Mechanica is attacking her town and Hidomi discovers a secret within her that could save everyone, a secret that only Haruko can unlock.<br>\nBut why did Haruko return to Earth? \nWhat happened to her Rickenbacker 4001 she left with Naota? \nAnd where did the human-type robot ‘Canti’ go?<br><br>\n(Source: Adult Swim)', 0, 1, 'FLCL 2, Furi Kuri Progressive, Fooly Cooly Progressive', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":6,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 187, 1, 23, 6, 21746, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21746-DTTSs6ChypxZ.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1305, 'Peacemaker Kurogane: Belief', 'PEACE MAKER 鐵 ～オモウミチ～', NULL, 'A new anime adaptation of the Peace Maker Kurogane manga.\n<br><br>\nAlthough traumatized by witnessing the murder of his parents by one of the Choushuu, Ichimura Tetsunosuke\'s thirst for revenge leads him to desire strength. At the age of 15, Tetsunosuke approached the Shinsengumi, wanting to become one of its members. However, Tetsunosuke lacked the skill, mind, and will to emotionlessly cut down whoever threatened peace and the Shinsengumi. Even with the support of his brother Tatsunosuke and his newfound friends of the Shinsengumi, little did Tetsunosuke know the blood and pain he would have to face being part of this historical group.', 0, 1, 'Peacemaker Kurogane', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":6,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 15, 1, 60, 1, 21770, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx21770-GgEnnkspM7gW.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1306, 'Inazuma Eleven Ares', 'イナズマイレブン アレスの天秤', NULL, 'Ares no Tenbin depicts an alternative canon following the events of the first season of the original Inazuma Eleven anime. Taking place sometime after Raimon\'s victory in the Football Frontier, in this alternative universe, the alien attack from the second season never occurs. Japanese soccer has been deemed weak compared to international competition. Due to this, the Raimon Eleven have been disbanded, and its members are sent to different soccer teams across Japan in the hopes of strengthening Japan\'s soccer at a national level. Moreover, in the modern world of Japanese youth soccer, sponsorship has become a vital aspect of a team\'s survival. A youth team must have a sponsor, otherwise, their club will face disbandment, and are not permitted to partake in matches.<br><br>\n\nThe series focuses on the forward Asuto Inamori and his team, Inakuni Raimon, which is made up of players from the remote Inakunijima Island. They have replaced the original Raimon Eleven as Raimon Junior High\'s soccer team, and are competing as underdogs in the annual Football Frontier youth tournament.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Wikpedia)', 0, 1, 'Inazuma Eleven Balance of Ares', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 86, 1, 23, 26, 21879, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/21879-Ac6WnBmgL5T0.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1307, 'Dances with the Dragons', 'されど罪人は竜と踊る', NULL, 'The story revolves around \"jushiki\" (lit. spell equations), the equations that govern the quantum constant \"h\" of action, change the laws of physics at the local scale, give birth to TNT explosives and poison gas, and cause incredible physical phenomena such as plasma and nuclear fusion. Two \"jushikishi\" (spell equationists) who use jushiki in battle are Gayus (who deals with bad luck with tact) and the beautiful but cruel sword-wielder Gigina. These two bounty hunters are caught up in a battle with dragons in the city of Eridana and in the intrigue of great nations.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 41, 1, 24, 12, 87504, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx87504-2RlSzxZc6tT9.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1308, 'ハイスクールD×D HERO', 'null', NULL, 'The fourth season of <i>High School DxD</i>.<br><br>Issei and the 2nd years attend a class trip to Kyoto for well-deserved relaxation, leaving the senior and junior class students of the Gremory family behind. However, once there, they fall under attack and must win without Rias or their other powerhouses.<br><br>(Source: Anime News Network)<br><br>\n<i>Includes episode 0, Taiikukan-ura no Holy</i>.', 2, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 1480, 1, 24, 13, 97767, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/97767-Akkp9Alo4ut4.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1309, 'Isekai Izakaya: Japanese Food From Another World', '異世界居酒屋～古都アイテーリアの居酒屋のぶ～', NULL, 'Izakaya “Nobu” is a modest establishment, staffed by only two people: master, Nobuyuki Yazawa, and server, Shinobu Senke.<br>\n<br>\nDespite its humble appearance, its entrance is mysteriously connected to an ancient city from another world: “Aitheria.” Nobu’s patrons consist of lazy palace guards, incognito clergymen, and the Waterworks Guildmaster – certainly not your average clientele!<br>\n<br>\nBut once they enter Nobu’s doors, they are greeted with the finest alcohol they’ve ever tasted and dishes the likes of which they’ve never seen. With the food plentiful and the drinks flowing, the patrons leave their troubles at the door as they call, “Give me a cold ale, master!”<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 1, 1, 'isekai izakaya \"NOBU\", Otherwordly Izakaya \"Nobu\"', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 119, 1, 15, 24, 97873, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/97873-XWts5ea1rs1n.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1310, 'LOST SONG', 'LOST SONG', NULL, 'Rin, an energetic girl who loves to eat, lives in a verdant frontier village. Deep within the royal palace in the bustling capital city, the songstress Finis spends her days in solitude. Both share a special power no other person has. A miraculous power that can heal wounds, create water and stir the wind -- the power of song. Guided by destiny, the two young women each face an arduous journey with the power of song. The shadow of war looms over the kingdom, tainting even the miraculous songs with the blood of innocents. Loved ones meet their deaths as silent screams echo through a stone prison. As two destinies intersect, will the final song be one of despair, hope or...?<br><br>\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Finis, La Canción Perdida', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":31,\"month\":3,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 144, 1, 24, 12, 98073, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/98073-UfShL8KfCuwr.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1311, 'Lostorage conflated WIXOSS', 'Lostorage conflated WIXOSS', NULL, 'The second season of <i>Lostorage incited WIXOSS</i>. <br><br>\n\nThe peaceful days turn out to be short-lived as the shadow of another Selector Battle looms large. Kiyoi Mizushima is the first to notice that things are amiss, and she makes her move to put an end to the cycle of darkness.The Battle this time includes a new card, \"Key,\" and has been set up with rules different than before. With both the mastermind and their motive shrouded in mystery, the darkness grows ever deeper and more menacing. Suzuko Homura, Chinatsu Morishita, Hanna Mikage, Ruuko Kominato, Yuzuki Kurebayashi, Hitoe Uemura, and Akira Aoi, the Selectors gather once again.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 68, 1, 23, 12, 98473, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx98473-1Sge8XSDWtoY.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1312, 'Gurazeni: Money Pitch', 'グラゼニ', NULL, 'The \"baseball money survival\" story focuses on a baseball team that operates as a highly-stratified society, where the player\'s performance determines his annual salary. The story follows an eight-year relief pitcher with an odd left-handed side-arm throw as he fights to survive under the team\'s strict system.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Money Diamond', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 8, 1, 24, 12, 98479, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/98479-BCnglozOlch3.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1313, 'Umamusume: Pretty Derby', 'ウマ娘 プリティーダービー', NULL, 'In a world very much like our own, great race horses of the past have a chance to be reborn as \"horse girls\"—girls with the ears and tails of horses as well as their speed and endurance. The best of these horse girls go to train at Tokyo\'s Tracen Academy, hopefully moving on to fame and fortune as both racers and idols.<br>\n<br>\nSpecial Week, a high school horse girl from the countryside, has just transferred to Tracen, and she\'s determined to fulfill her promise to her mother to become the best horse girl in Japan. On her way to school, she takes a pit stop at the race track and instantly falls in love with Silence Suzuka\'s style, becoming determined to race on the same team as her.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 2, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 424, 1, 24, 13, 98514, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/98514-U5VS9j3Thd92.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1314, 'Comic Girls', 'こみっくがーるず', NULL, 'The manga\'s story centers on the 15-year-old high school student and manga creator Kaoruko Moeta, who uses the pen name Chaos. After ranking at the bottom of a reader survey, Kaoruko\'s editor recommends that she enter an all-female dormitory for manga creators. Kaoruko\'s roommates are shoujo manga creator Koyume Koizuka, teen romance manga creator Ruki Irokawa, and shounen manga creator Tsubasa Katsuki. The girls support each other as they work to become better manga creators.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 552, 1, 24, 12, 99131, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/99131-xQSIHqKTUmCc.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1315, '曇天に笑う<外伝> ～宿命、双頭の風魔～', 'null', NULL, 'The second part in an anime film trilogy adaptation of the Donten ni Warau Gaiden (Laughing Under the Clouds - Side Story) spinoff manga.', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":6,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 26, 1, 60, 1, 99196, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx99196-Ovstu6Hl0K0B.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1316, 'Chi\'s Sweet Adventure Season 2', 'Koneko no Chii: Ponponra Daibouken 2', NULL, 'The second season of the new 3DCG anime series for Koneko no Chii.', 0, 1, 'こねこのチー ポンポンらー大冒険 2, Koneko no Chii: Ponponra Daibouken 2', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 5, 1, 12, 25, 99478, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx99478-51yPecTKIGaN.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1317, 'Devils\' Line', 'デビルズライン', NULL, 'Everything you thought you knew about vampires is wrong. They can walk in the daylight and holy water doesn\'t burn them. In fact, vampires can pass as normal humans so perfectly that even other vampires have trouble spotting them. Until they drink human blood, that is; then they transform into monstrous beasts who mindlessly rape and murder. But not all vampires are evil. The secret task force that patrols Tokyo\'s vampire population has several fanged operatives, including half-human Yuuki Anzai, who believes that his human heritage lets him resist his species\' basest cravings. But after Yuuki rescues college student Tsukasa Taira from a vampire stalker, he realizes that he\'s succumbing to urges he\'s never felt before.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)', 0, 1, 'Devil\'s Line', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 922, 1, 24, 12, 99531, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/99531-2a6S5b39anMV.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1318, 'Vatican Miracle Examiner (OVA)', 'バチカン奇跡調査官 魔女のスープ', NULL, 'The flyer from this year\'s AnimeJapan 2017 event revealed that Vatican Kiseki Chousakan will receive an OVA episode.', 0, 1, 'Vatican Miracle Examiner Special, Vatican Kiseki Chousakan (2018), バチカン奇跡調査官 (2018), Vatican Kiseki Chousakan OVA', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":11,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 5, 1, 25, 1, 99568, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx99568-le1iw1iNLxyy.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1319, 'Wotakoi: Love is Hard for Otaku', 'ヲタクに恋は難しい', NULL, 'Having slept through all four of her alarms, the energetic Narumi Momose finds herself running late for her first day of work at a new office. As she races to catch her train, she makes a promise to herself that none of her coworkers will find out about her dark secret: that she is an otaku and a fujoshi. Her plan goes instantly awry, though, when she runs into Hirotaka Nifuji, an old friend from middle school. Although she tries to keep her secret by inviting him out for drinks after work, her cover is blown when he casually asks her whether or not she will be attending the upcoming Summer Comiket. Luckily for her, the only witnesses—Hanako Koyanagi and Tarou Kabakura—are otaku as well.<br>\n<br>\nLater that night, the pair go out for drinks so that they can catch up after all the years apart. After Narumi complains about her previous boyfriend breaking up with her because he refused to date a fujoshi, Hirotaka suggests that she try dating a fellow otaku, specifically himself. He makes a solemn promise to always be there for her, to support her, and to help her farm for rare drops in Monster Hunter. Blown away by the proposal, Narumi agrees immediately. Thus the two otaku start dating, and their adorably awkward romance begins.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)', 8, 1, 'Otaku ni Koi wa Muzukashii, WotaKoi, It’s Difficult to Love an Otaku, Love is Hard for an Otaku, Love is Hard for Nerds, ווטקוי: האהבה קשה לאוטאקו, 阿宅的恋爱真难, ยากแท้จริงหนอรักของโอตาคุ', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 6737, 1, 23, 11, 99578, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/99578-8orFGgDq7NS8.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1320, 'Alice or Alice', 'ありすorありす ～シスコン兄さんと双子の妹～', NULL, 'What happens when a big brother idolizes his little twin sisters? All sorts of mischief that’s what! Meet Rise and Airi, twin sisters who love to hang out with their friends, go to cute pastry shops and annoy their big brother. Watch as these adorable pint-size girls learn to navigate through life while making sure their brother doesn’t go too over the top.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)', 0, 1, 'Alice or Alice: A Siscon Brother and His Twin Sisters', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 40, 1, 3, 12, 99638, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/99638-PcdUkCWjUz5j.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1321, 'PERSONA5 the Animation', 'PERSONA5 the Animation', NULL, 'Ren Amamiya is about to enter his second year after transferring to Shujin Academy in Tokyo.<br>\nFollowing a particular incident, his Persona awakens, and together with his friends they form the “Phantom Thieves of Hearts” to reform hearts of corrupt adults by stealing the source of their distorted desires.<br>\nMeanwhile, bizarre and inexplicable crimes have been popping up one after another…<br>\nLiving an ordinary high school life in Tokyo during the day, the group maneuvers the metropolitan city as Phantom Thieves after hours.<br>\nLet the curtain rise for this grand, picaresque story!\n<br><br>\n(Source: Official website)', 1, 1, 'P5A, ペルソナ5アニメーション', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 566, 1, 24, 26, 99693, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/99693-b3wrYly0eEa6.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1322, 'Golden Kamuy', 'ゴールデンカムイ', NULL, 'In the early twentieth century, Russo-Japanese War veteran Saichi “Immortal” Sugimoto scratches out a meager existence during the postwar gold rush in the wilderness of Hokkaido. When he stumbles across a map to a fortune in hidden Ainu gold, he sets off on a treacherous quest to find it. But Sugimoto is not the only interested party, and everyone who knows about the gold will kill to possess it! Faced with the harsh conditions of the northern wilderness, ruthless criminals and rogue Japanese soldiers, Sugimoto will need all his skills and luck—and the help of an Ainu girl named Asirpa—to survive.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Viz Media)', 2, 1, 'Golden Kamui, 黄金神威', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 1587, 1, 24, 12, 99699, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/99699-95D2XWA6eWAH.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo');
