(1323, 'Kase-san and Morning Glories', 'あさがおと加瀬さん。', NULL, 'A relationship is like a garden. It\'s hard, really hard, to plant the initial seeds. Once you\'ve gone through the agonizing process of wondering if the other person even likes you, fought the fear that telling her could destroy everything, and made your confession, the most difficult part begins. Because you have to keep nurturing this wonderful new feeling to keep it growing. Not just in your own heart, but in hers. And since even the most beautiful rose can cut you to the bone with its thorns, who can you talk to for advice? Especially when you\'re both girls in high school? For shy Yamada and boyish Kase, time is running out.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)', 2, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":6,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 780, 1, 59, 1, 99916, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/99916-A1CqNrdSMHM4.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1324, 'Libra of Nil Admirari', 'ニル・アドミラリの天秤', NULL, 'The Taishou era didn’t end in 15 years, but went on for another 25.<br><br>\n\nIn order to protect her waning family, a girl resolves to marry a man she doesn’t even know the name of. However, just before the marriage was to take place, the girl’s younger brother mysteriously committed suicide by self-immolation and was found holding an old book in his hands.<br><br>\n\nAppearing before the bewildered young girl was the “Imperial Library Intelligence Asset Management Bureau”- more commonly referred to as “Fukurou”.<br><br>\n\nAccording to these men, there exists “Maremono”, which are books that greatly affects its readers. On top of that, ever since the incident involving the girl’s younger brother, she unwittingly gains the ability to see “Auras” (the sentiments of the Maremono which manifest as bright lights and are usually invisible to humans). It was as though fate were trying to drag the young girl in its flames.<br><br>\n\nAnd then, even though apprehensive, the girl chooses to venture outside her bird cage.<br><br>\n\nJealousy, hatred, scorn, compassion and love.\nWhat awaited the girl was the darkness of betrayal that had already begun to bewitchingly inlay the imperial capital.<br><br>\n\nToyed by and swayed within that darkness, will the young girl finally reach the truth after her struggles, or…?<br><br>\n\n(Source: VNDB)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 58, 1, 23, 12, 99963, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/99963-JCefe2KfQj0y.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1325, 'Space Battleship Tiramisu', '宇宙戦艦ティラミス', NULL, 'The human race extended it\'s life field and greed to the vast reaches of space... In Space Era 0156, a war breaks out amidst all of the colonies. Earth begins to construct a new space battleship called Tiramisu in secret. Just as the war begins, one genius pilot steers the Tiramisu as a beacon of hope for humanity.\n', 0, 1, 'Uchuu Senkan Tiramisù', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 49, 1, 7, 13, 100009, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100009-KUxEsZ8NTUzY.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1326, 'MAGICAL GIRL SITE', '魔法少女サイト', NULL, 'Asagiri Aya is a young girl who has fallen victim to bullies at her school. Looking for a way to escape her troubles, she looks to the internet for distraction, when a mysterious website called \"Magical Girl Site\" appears. Simply viewing the page is all it takes to hurtle Aya headlong into the deadly world of the Magical Girl Apocalypse. There, it’s fight or die, against a seemingly endless array of savagely adorable, frilly-skirted killing machines, each armed with magical powers and an unquenchable thirst for blood and chaos. \n<br><br>\n(Source: Seven Seas Entertainment)', 0, 1, 'Garota Mágica .Com', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 637, 1, 25, 12, 100010, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100010-WZMK7JXMAi2i.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1327, 'HINAMATSURI', 'ヒナまつり', NULL, 'The comedy manga centers around a super-powered girl named Hina and Nitta, a young member of the yakuza. Hina suddenly appears in Nitta\'s room and threatens him with her extraordinary powers. However, they end up living together.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 3, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 2583, 1, 24, 12, 100077, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100077-XKMTrxaMGhBj.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1328, 'Butlers x Battlers', 'Butlers～千年百年物語～', NULL, 'Koma Jinguji (Jay) is the smart and handsome student council president. His elegant smile captures the hearts of women. Tsubasa Hayakawa is a multi-talented and gentle shop assistant at a café. His cafe latte with owl latte art is very popular with female customers. The two men travel through time to fight their archenemy. The charming \"Butlers,\" as they are called, fight supernatural battles and also experience a slapstick comedic life at their academy.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":12,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 29, 1, 23, 12, 100083, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx100083-TdvGpOG6ZYZP.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1329, 'My Hero Academia Season 3', '僕のヒーローアカデミア 3', NULL, 'Summer is here, and the heroes of Class 1-A and 1-B are in for the toughest training camp of their lives! A group of seasoned pros pushes everyone\'s Quirks to new heights as the students face one overwhelming challenge after another. Braving the elements in this secret location becomes the least of their worries when routine training turns into a critical struggle for survival.<br><br>(Source: Crunchyroll)', 11, 1, 'BNHA 3, MHA 3, 我的英雄学院 3, 我的英雄学院第三季', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 9220, 1, 24, 25, 100166, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100166-k7RXwN5vZg0r.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1330, 'Liz and the Blue Bird', 'リズと青い鳥', NULL, 'Students and best friends Mizore Yoroizuka and Nozomi Kasaki prepare to play a complex musical duet, <i>Liz and the Blue Bird</i>, for oboe and flute. Though they play beautifully together and have been friends since childhood, Mizore and Nozomi find that with graduation looming and the duet proving difficult, their friendship begins to buckle under the pressure. Interspersed with their story is the fantasy tale of Liz, drawn like a storybook, contrasting with the crisp realism of the school.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Shout! Factory)', 2, 1, 'Liz und ein Blauer Vogel,  Liz et l\'Oiseau bleu, 莉茲與青鳥', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":21,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 2007, 1, 90, 1, 100178, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100178-pneDY2KoVnbz.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1331, 'Tada Never Falls In Love', '多田くんは恋をしない', NULL, 'Mitsuyoshi Tada, a boy who has never known love, is taking pictures of the cherry blossoms in full bloom when he meets Teresa Wagner, a transfer student from Luxembourg. Upon arriving in Japan, she got lost, separated from her travel companion. Mitsuyoshi helps her and brings her to his grandfather\'s coffee shop.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Tadakun wa Koi wo Shinai, Tadakoi, Tada-kun Never Falls In Love', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 791, 1, 24, 13, 100179, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100179-LV2oqGihvbjN.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1332, 'Digimon Adventure tri. Chapter 6: Our Future', 'デジモンアドベンチャー tri. 第6章「ぼくらの未来」', NULL, 'The sixth movie in the new Digimon Adventure series.', 0, 1, 'Digimon tri. 6', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":5,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 61, 1, 98, 1, 100181, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100181-FQQPfwq66cWY.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1333, 'Sword Art Online Alternative: Gun Gale Online', 'ソードアート・オンライン オルタナティブ ガンゲイル・オンライン', NULL, 'The story follows Karen Kohiruimaki, a 183-centimeter-tall (6-foot-tall) college student who\'s insecure about her height, and is bad at dealing with people in the real world. She enters the world of Gun Gale Online with her avatar, Ren, who is less than 150 centimeters (5 feet) tall and wears all pink. She meets a beautiful, brown-skinned female player who goes by Pitohui. They hit it off, but one day Pitohui pressures her to participate in \"Squad Jam,\" a team battle royale variation of the Bullet of Bullets tournament.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 1, 1, 'SAO Alternative: Gun Gale Online', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 1398, 1, 24, 12, 100183, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100183-RMVkUK9IC5Au.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1334, 'Tokyo Ghoul:re', '東京喰種-トーキョーグール-:re', NULL, 'Two years have passed since the CCG’s raid on Anteiku. Although the atmosphere in Tokyo has changed drastically due to the increased influence of the CCG, ghouls continue to pose a problem as they have begun taking caution, especially the terrorist organization Aogiri Tree, who acknowledge the CCG’s growing threat to their existence.\nThe creation of a special team, known as the Quinx Squad, may provide the CCG with the push they need to exterminate Tokyo’s unwanted residents. As humans who have undergone surgery in order to make use of the special abilities of ghouls, they participate in operations to eradicate the dangerous creatures. The leader of this group, Haise Sasaki, is a half-ghoul, half-human who has been trained by famed special class investigator, Kishou Arima. However, there’s more to this young man than meets the eye, as unknown memories claw at his mind, slowly reminding him of the person he used to be.', 3, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 2305, 1, 24, 12, 100240, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n100240-UuzeDXFw7itH.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1335, 'Batman Ninja', 'ニンジャバットマン', NULL, 'Gorilla Grodd\'s time displacement machine transports many of Batman\'s worst enemies to feudal Japan - along with the Dark Knight and a few of his allies. The villains take over the forms of the feudal lords that rule the divided land, with the Joker taking the lead among the warring factions. As his traditional high-tech weaponry is exhausted almost immediately, Batman must rely on his intellect and his allies - including Catwoman and the extended Bat-family - to restore order to the land, and return to present-day Gotham City.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":24,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 92, 1, 85, 1, 100248, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100248-N2GCWVR4G0W0.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1336, '奴隷区 The Animation', 'null', NULL, 'What if you could enslave anyone you ever wanted? Well, this comes close. The SCM lets you enslave anyone who is also wearing an SCM, at a price. One must win over the other, at the cost of anything, in order for the other to become their slave.\n', 0, 1, 'Doreiku - Boku to Nijuusannin no Dorei, 23slaves and me, Dorei-ku: Boku to 23-nin no Dorei', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 62, 1, 24, 12, 100251, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100251-6HSLsotFOecT.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1337, 'Megalobox', 'メガロボクス', NULL, '\"To be quiet and do as you\'re told, that\'s the cowardly choice.\" These are the words of Junk Dog, an underground fighter of Megalo Box, an evolution of boxing that utilizes mechanical limbs known as Gear to enhance the speed and power of its users. Despite the young man\'s brimming potential as a boxer, the illegal nature of his participation forces him to make a living off of throwing matches as dictated by his boss Gansaku Nanbu. However, this all changes when the Megalo Box champion Yuuri enters his shabby ring under the guise of just another challenger. Taken out in a single round, Junk Dog is left with a challenge: \"If you\'re serious about fighting me again, then fight your way up to me and my ring.\"<br>\n<br>\nFilled with overwhelming excitement and backed by the criminal syndicate responsible for his thrown matches, Junk Dog enters Megalonia: a world-spanning tournament that will decide the strongest Megalo Boxer of them all. Having no name of his own, he takes on the moniker of \"Joe\" as he begins his climb from the very bottom of the ranked list of fighters. With only three months left to qualify, Joe must face off against opponents the likes of which he has never fought in order to meet the challenge of his rival.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 1976, 1, 25, 13, 100298, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100298-vOjmw7DvMns3.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1338, 'MAJOR 2nd', 'メジャー2nd', NULL, 'Shigeno Daigo is an elementary student whose father, Goro, is a professional baseball player. Inspired by his father, who was once a Major League player, Daigo started playing baseball with the Mifune Dolphins, a youth team. However, he was unable to live up to the expectations of being the son of a professional, and quit baseball after less than a year. Then, in the spring of his sixth-grade year, Daigo\'s school welcomes a transfer student, Sato Hikaru, whose father is Sato Toshiya, a former Major League player and Goro\'s close friend. The fate of these two young men begins to move forward!<br><br>(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, 'メジャーセカンド', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 58, 1, 24, 25, 100306, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100306-15AYgi4A4ghv.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1339, 'LAST HOPE', '重神機パンドーラ', NULL, 'In the year 2031, an experimental energy device known as the \"Quantum Reactor\" is created to help alleviate the problems stemming from Earth\'s dwindling fossil fuel reserves. Unfortunately, the \"Quantum Reactor\" goes out of control, exploding and bathing the world with unknown energies in an incident known as the \"Shouryuu Crisis\". As a result of the catastrophic environmental changes that follow, humanity is pushed to the brink of extinction, and strange new organisms - part organic, part mechanical - known as the \"B.R.A.I.\" emerge.<br><br>\n\nSeven years later, Leon Lau - one of the scientists at the center of the \"Shouryuu Crisis\", is living in the wilderness near Neo Shouryou, one of the last remaining human cities. Leon has entered into a \"family contract\" with Chloe Lau, and together the two of them research their own methods of combatting the B.R.A.I. threat.<br><br>\n\n(Source: CR)', 0, 1, 'الأمل الأخير, 重神机潘多拉', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":29,\"month\":3,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 27, 1, 23, 26, 100341, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx100341-0fgk2fX8hc79.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1340, 'SNSポリス', 'null', NULL, 'The story centers around the titular \"SNS Police\" (Social Network Service Police), who protect the peace in social media sites like Twitter and Facebook and deal harsh justice to those who violate it.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":24,\"month\":3,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 5, 9, 100400, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx100400-xTwLZlUtdxAB.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1341, 'Forest of Piano', 'ピアノの森 (TV)', NULL, 'A tranquil tale about two boys from very different upbringings. On one hand you have Kai, born as the son of a prostitute, who\'s been playing the abandoned piano in the forest near his home ever since he was young. And on the other you have Shuuhei, practically breast-fed by the piano as the son of a family of prestigious pianists. Yet it is their common bond with the piano that eventually intertwines their paths in life.<br><br>\n\n(Source: KEFI)', 0, 1, 'Piano Forest, The Perfect World of Kai, El Bosque del Piano, יער הפסנתר, بيانو', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 289, 1, 25, 12, 100401, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100401-ox7dBr8i1q35.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1342, 'Fist of the Blue Sky: Regenesis', '蒼天の拳REGENESIS', NULL, 'A mysterious man known as \"the King of Death\" roams the streets of pre-war Shanghai in this action-packed prequel to Fist of the North Star.<br><br>\nShanghai in the 1930s is a dangerous place. Foreign governments and Chinese factions have carved the city into different quarters, each with its own laws and government, and all rife with corruption. As the major powers vie for political control, the streets are left to local gangs. Life is cheap, and death is always near.<br><br>\nIn days past, one man walked these mean streets battling the forces of evil. He was known only as Yan Wang, \"the King of Death.\" Few knew who he really was, but many knew that he was a master of Hokuto Shinken - Fist of the North Star - a lethal martial art. He disappeared years ago after dispatching the city\'s worst gangsters, and is now rumored to be in Japan. Various people have come to Japan in search of him, but who will find him first?', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 11, 1, 22, 12, 100408, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n100408-mVRLyO5Aq8ML.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1343, 'Kakuriyo -Bed & Breakfast for Spirits-', 'かくりよの宿飯', NULL, 'The series centers on a female college student named Aoi, who inherited the ability to see spirits from her late grandfather. Aoi prides herself on her cooking, and one day she\'s feeding some agricultural spirits when suddenly a god and the master of the \"Tenshinya\" (Heavenly Inn) appears and takes Aoi away. He says that due to her grandfather\'s debts, she must become his bride. Aoi hates this idea and instead declares that she will pay back her grandfather\'s debt by working at the Tenshinya. \n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 513, 1, 23, 26, 100500, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100500-oP4JhVMZsnE7.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1344, 'Real Girl', '3D彼女 リアルガール', NULL, 'Hikari Tsutsui has never been popular, his one real friend is an even worse otaku than he is, and the only girls he\'s known are the two-dimensional women from his manga and video games. Until, that is, he\'s sent to help clean the pool as punishment and is partnered with the school\'s resident \"bad girl\", the very real, very three-dimensional Iroha Igarashi. Brash, beautiful, and known for her promiscuous behavior, Iroha is loathed by other girls but loved by the guys. And yet, inexplicably, she not only seems to be interested in Hikari, but proposes that they enter into a relationship! Unable to resist, Hikari agrees, but there\'s one big catch - Iroha\'s moving away in six months, so no matter what happens between them, in half a year Hikari\'s guaranteed to lose his REAL GIRL!<br><br>\n\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)', 2, 1, '3D Girlfriend, Three D Kanojo Real Girl', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 846, 1, 23, 12, 100526, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100526-the6isOYqR8S.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1345, 'Amanchu! ~Advance~', 'あまんちゅ！～あどばんす～', NULL, 'The second season of <i>Amanchu!</i><br><br>Hikari Kohinata and Futaba Ooki have together found joy in many things through scuba diving and the most everyday of events. Hikari was born and brought up in a small oceanside town on Izu, and Futaba moved there from Tokyo, but the two polar opposites met at Yumegaoka High and instantly hit it off. The always-reserved Futaba found her perfect foil in the cheery and optimistic Hikari, and their friendship gave her the courage to take the first step and experience many of the smaller joys in life. She also took the Open Water Diver exam and passed, and now she has her sights set on the Advanced Open Water Diver certification.<br><br>(Source: Anime News Network)', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 59, 1, 24, 12, 100532, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100532-jNIiT1GR40wk.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1346, 'SERVAMP -サーヴァンプ-: Alice in the Garden', 'null', NULL, 'Movie based on the SERVAMP manga series.', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 45, 1, 60, 1, 100537, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx100537-mwl7hyhz9cEN.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1347, 'Godzilla: City on the Edge of Battle', 'GODZILLA -決戦機動増殖都市-', NULL, 'On Earth, Haruo and his companions make contact with the indigenous Houtua tribe. To defeat Godzilla, they set out for the old Mechagodzilla facility.<br><br>Source: Netflix', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":18,\"month\":5,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 51, 1, 101, 1, 100561, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100561-ufEJIM2I13ho.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1348, 'カリギュラ', 'null', NULL, 'The Caligula Effect is set in a virtual reality program known as \"Mobius\", created so people can escape pain in their lives and live in an idyllic high school setting, forced to live out their 3 years Indefinitely. The main protagonist is one of a group who realize that they are in a virtual world, and form the \"Go-Home Club\", a group dedicated to escaping from Mobius and its god-like overseer program, a vocal program called \"μ\". They oppose the \"Ostinato Musicians\", a group who supports μ and sees the Go-Home Club as traitors.', 0, 1, 'The Caligula Effect', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 97, 1, 24, 12, 100569, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100569-t2MhiAvBGphp.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1349, 'My Sweet Tyrant', 'あっくんとカノジョ', NULL, 'The romantic comedy follows the everyday life of an extremely tsundere boy named Atsuhiro \"Akkun\" Kagari and his girlfriend Non \"Nontan\" Katagiri. Akkun\'s behavior is harsh towards Nontan with verbal abuse and neglect, but he actually is head-over-heels for her and habitually acts like a stalker by tailing her or eavesdropping. Nontan is oblivious to Akkun\'s stalker ways, and thinks his actions are cute.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 1, 1, 'Akkun and His Girlfriend', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":6,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 313, 1, 4, 25, 100645, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100645-aV3mNej24VMq.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1350, 'Case Closed: Zero the Enforcer', '名探偵コナン ゼロの執行人', NULL, 'There is a sudden explosion at Tokyo Summit\'s giant Edge of Ocean facility. The shadow of Touru Amuro, who works for the National Police Agency Security Bureau as Zero, appears at the site. In addition, the \"triple-face\" character known as Rei Furuya, a detective, and Kogorou Mouri\'s apprentice, is also known as Bourbon, a Black Organization member. Kogorou is arrested as a suspect in the case of the explosion. Conan conducts an investigation to prove Kogorou\'s innocence, but Amuro gets in his way.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Detective Conan: Zero the Enforcer, Detective Conan Movie 22: Zero no Shikkounin, Detective Conan Movie 22: Zero\'s Executioner, Meitantei Conan Movie 22: Zero no Shikkounin, Detektiv Conan: Zero der Vollstrecker, Case Closed Movie 22: Zero Executor, 名侦探柯南：零的执行人', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":14,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 55, 1, 115, 1, 100653, '2021-11-30 11:20:06', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n100653-zxyI1eDBJjJz.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1351, 'Dragon Pilot: Hisone & Masotan', 'ひそねとまそたん', NULL, 'Straightforward and innocent Hisone Amakasu is a Self-Defense Force rookie stationed at the Air Self-Defense Force\'s Gifu Base. She was struggling with the fact that she sometimes hurts people unintentionally by her innocent words and decided to join the Air Self-Defence Force, hoping to maintain a certain distance from people. This decision led her to a fateful encounter which profoundly changed her life. It was the \"OTF\" dragon hidden in the base and it chose Hisone as his pilot. When it soared into the sky with Hisone, her fate as a dragon pilot was decided. It is said that dragons have a key to the future of the world…<br><br>\n\n(Source: Official website)', 0, 1, 'HisoMaso, Hisone y Masotan: A Lomos del Dragón, Pilotos de Dragão - Hisone to Masotan, هيسونا والتنين', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 288, 1, 25, 12, 100673, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n100673-R0BsjQx7erc8.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1352, 'Magical Girl Ore', '魔法少女 俺', NULL, 'This story is about a 15-year-old girl who is a newbie idol in love with her best friend\'s brother who is also a popular idol. But she runs into a scary yakuza guy and finds out that her mother was an ex-magical girl, and the yakuza was her mascot. Her love interest gets kidnapped by demons that look like burly men with cute squirrel heads. So she contracts the yakuza to become a magical girl, which in this story means she turns into a handsome guy in a magical girl outfit. On top of that, her love interest shows an attraction toward her magical guy form. Her best friend turns out to be in love with her and also becomes a magical cross-dressing guy to save her life.<br></br>\n\nThus, their manager, who is a magical girl geek, then decides to turn them into an idol unit.<br></br>\n', 0, 1, 'Magical Girl Boy', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 110, 1, 23, 12, 100715, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n100715-7tDNq0BrGUIN.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1353, 'Yotsuiro Biyori', '鹿楓堂よついろ日和', NULL, 'Four men—Gure, Sui, Tokitaka, and Tsubaki—each help run a Japanese tea shop together called Rokuhoudou. When one visits the shop, they are greeted warmly, is served tea, and are often helped with any problems they may have.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime\'s Website)', 0, 1, '鹿枫堂四色日和', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":11,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 107, 1, 23, 12, 100727, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100727-YBjnoGqtpJpo.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1354, 'Captain Tsubasa (2018)', 'キャプテン翼', NULL, 'Remake of the first series.  \n<br><br>\nTsubasa Oozora is an 11-year-old elementary school student who is deeply in love with football and dreams of one day winning the FIFA World Cup for Japan. He lives together with his mother in Japan, while his father is a seafaring captain who travels around the world. Tsubasa Ozora moves to the town Nankatsu to increase his skills as a soccer player. He is challenged by the Super Goalkeeper Genzo Wakabayashi. He then agrees to compete and see who was the best soccer player there.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 170, 1, 24, 52, 100745, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100745-O7IJXNebsrK1.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1356, 'Love To-LIE-Angle', '立花館To Lieあんぐる', NULL, 'When Natsuno Hanabi went back to her hometown to study in high school, she thought that she will have a new wonderful life. But Tachibanakan, the dormitory she was going to live in, was not what she expected.', 0, 1, 'Tachibanakan Triangle', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 74, 1, 4, 12, 100762, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100762-WpONqVuUaUIl.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1357, 'Food Wars! The Third Plate: Totsuki Train Arc', '『食戟のソーマ 餐ノ皿』 遠月列車篇', NULL, 'The second half of the third season of <i>Shokugeki no Souma</i>.<br>\n<br>\nA dark age of cooking befalls Tootsuki Culinary Academy. With the Elite Ten\'s devastating coup d\'état, Azami Nakiri is now the director of the prestigious school. Students must now conform to Azami\'s ideology of \"true gourmet food\" and are forbidden to express creativity, or else face expulsion.<br>\n<br>\nHowever, Souma Yukihira and the members of the Polar Star Dormitory refuse to accept these changes. Aided by other rebellious first-years, including the tenth seat, Erina Nakiri, Souma and his allies band together to fight off supporters of Azami\'s regime. But corrupt instructors and the menacing Central organization stand in their way, and so they must work together, harder than ever before, to survive every underhanded plot designed to banish them from the school.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)', 3, 1, '食戟之灵 餐之皿 远月列车篇', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 1499, 1, 24, 12, 100773, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100773-VB3awsuL4K34.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1358, 'Layton Mystery Detective Agency: Kat\'s Mystery-Solving Files', 'レイトン ミステリー探偵社～カトリーのナゾトキファイル～', NULL, '50 Puzzling Episodes, One Gentlewoman Extraordinaire and a Whole Load of New Mysteries coming to the small screen in 2018!\n<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Picarats)', 0, 1, 'レイトン教授, Layton-kyouju, Professor Layton: The TV Series', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 45, 1, 23, 50, 100785, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100785-O1D6VL1BmQWM.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1359, 'おしりたんてい', 'null', NULL, 'He\'s chivalrous, cunning, and his looks are anything \"butt\"...<br>\nMeet “Butt Detective”, a gentleman whose catch phrase is, \"Hmm...I smell a case.\"<br>\nEvery day, he poots the big city\'s cases to rest.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Toei Animation)', 0, 1, 'Butt Detective', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":5,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 20, 10, 100790, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx100790-2fDgKG7PWaWD.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1360, 'Cutie Honey Universe', 'Cutie Honey Universe', NULL, 'Honey Kisaragi appears to be an ordinary girl attending St. Chapel Academy, but in reality she\'s the \"Warrior of Love\" Cutie Honey, a super-powered android created by Dr. Kisaragi. Honey and her allies investigate the evil schemes of Panther Claw, a criminal secret society, but Honey doesn\'t realize that the leader of Panther Claw is already closer than she thinks...<br><br>\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, 'キューティーハニー, Cutey Honey Universe', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 22, 1, 23, 12, 100814, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100814-Qk1SRcvV0gpF.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
