(1362, 'Lupin the 3rd Part V', 'ルパン三世 PART5', NULL, 'A legendary thief deserves a legendary heist, and Lupin has set his sights on his biggest bounty yet: Marco Polo, a dark-web marketplace where criminals lurk and there’s money for the taking. But just as Lupin swipes his latest fortune and tries to make off with the goods, his hideout is inexplicably surrounded by Zenigata and his forces thanks to a new game that’s gone viral on social media. It has a very specific, very unfortunate objective, and the name of the game is “Arrest Lupin III”!\n<br><br>\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)', 1, 1, 'Lupin Sansei Part V, Lupin Sansei: Adventure in France', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 292, 1, 22, 24, 100957, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100957-cEQFsq1NY2LU.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1363, 'Ninja Girl & Samurai Master 3rd', '信長の忍び〜姉川・石山篇〜', NULL, 'The third season of <i>Nobunaga no Shinobi</i>.', 0, 1, 'Ninja Girl & Samurai Master ~Anegawa and Ishiyama Arc~', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":7,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 4, 1, 4, 26, 100966, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx100966-YjL4J8XYa93K.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1364, 'GeGeGe no Kitaro', 'ゲゲゲの鬼太郎(2018)', NULL, 'Nearly twenty years into the 21st century, people have forgotten the existence of Yokai. When a number of unexplainable phenomena plague adults of the human world with confusion and chaos, thirteen-year-old Mana writes a letter to the Yokai Post in search of answers, only to be greeted by Ge Ge Ge no Kitaro...<br> <br>(Source: Crunchyroll)', 1, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":1,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 102, 1, 23, 97, 100978, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/100978-aeBVxeEtnc1S.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1365, 'Crossing Time', '踏切時間', NULL, 'The omnibus manga tells a series of short stories about conversations young women have while waiting at railroad crossings.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Fumikirijikan', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 54, 1, 4, 12, 101002, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n101002-YvKet6fJ1oqe.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1367, 'Junji Ito Collection: Tomie', '伊藤潤二「コレクション」富江', NULL, 'Unaired episodes included with the second and third DVD sets of the TV anime.\n<br><br>\nTomie Kawakami is a femme fatale with long black hair and a beauty mark just under her left eye. She can seduce nearly any man, and drive them to murder as well, even though the victim is often Tomie herself. While one lover seeks to keep her for himself, another grows terrified of the immortal succubus. But soon they realize no matter how many times they kill her, the world will never be free of Tomie.\n<br><br>\n(Source: VIZ Media)', 0, 1, 'Tomie', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":27,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 87, 1, 10, 2, 101016, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101016-f5Ocy7TmJocH.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1371, 'ガンダムビルドダイバーズ', 'null', NULL, 'The Gunpla Force Battle Tournament is a big event held in GBN once per year. Competing in the final round are Avalon, led by the champion Kyoya Kujo, and the elite 7th Panzer Division led by the cunning Rommel. Starting with Kyoya\'s Gundam AGE II Magnum, a variety of Gunpla take to the field to determine which is the strongest force!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Gundam.info)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 36, 1, 24, 25, 101036, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101036-IOCaHzp9eC3n.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1372, 'You Don\'t Know Gunma Yet', 'お前はまだグンマを知らない', NULL, 'The comedy manga centers on Nori Kamitsuki, who moves from Chiba Prefecture to a fictionalized version of Gunma Prefecture northwest of Tokyo, and the story focuses on Gunma\'s culture. Before moving to Gunma, Kamitsuki only sees that the prefecture has a fearsome reputation on the net. Upon moving, he soon makes contact with the people who hold a strong love of Gunma\'s culture.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'YDKGY', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 2, 1, 4, 12, 101042, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx101042-ylAUwu6Fyr51.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1373, 'アイカツフレンズ!', 'null', NULL, '\"Let\'s go, together! Head for the goal, Diamond Friends!!\"<br><br>\n\nThe new anime will have a theme of \"Aikatsu with your friends!\" and will center on a new protagonist named Aine Yuuki, who is good at making friends, and is enrolled in Star Harmony Academy\'s general education track. She befriends Mio Minato, the school\'s top idol, and becomes an idol herself.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 61, 1, 24, 50, 101043, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101043-fUBNXfvhBHEt.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1374, 'Last Period: the journey to the end of the despair', 'ラストピリオド －終わりなき螺旋の物語－', NULL, 'The story takes place in a world where fantastic beasts called \"Spirals\" are born from isolation. Those who can defeat the beasts are called \"Periods.\" Haru is an apprentice Period who belongs to the Arc End 8th Branch. However, after a mysterious theft incident, there is an economic collapse, and the Arc End headquarters abandons the 8th Division, leaving only three Periods left, including Haru. Haru and the other two Periods start their work to rebuild the 8th Division.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":12,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 35, 1, 24, 12, 101044, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n101044-2QcwDXPiVsMr.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1375, 'Cute High Earth Defense Club HAPPY KISS!', '美男高校地球防衛部HAPPY KISS！', NULL, 'Several years have passed since Binan High\'s Earth Defense Club saved the world from an alien invasion that sought to sap the world of love—okay, maybe that\'s how it happened. The truth is that no one really remembers if something like that happened or not, and now five friends-of-convenience share the defunct Earth Defense clubroom to goof off after school. But even if they don\'t know the club\'s history, their gathering at the local bathhouse attracts the attention of another adorable extraterrestrial: Karurusu, the otter-prince of Honyaraland. As part of his planet\'s conquest initiative—\"tributary outreach program\"—Karurusu transforms these five misfits into magic knights who will bring happiness to all lost souls. Unfortunately, the fox-prince Rafunui has his own ideas about how to improve this Earth colony, empowering his own trio of dark knights to oppose this new batch of magical boys.<br><br>(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 16, 1, 24, 12, 101046, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101046-8Z67RQJv15gO.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1376, 'もしもし、てるみです。', 'null', NULL, 'The \"telephone romantic comedy\" follows a girl named Terumi, who works for a telephone company that has an anti-internet policy, and a middle school boy named Rintarō who is in love with her.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Moshimoshi,  Terumi Desu', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":6,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 1, 1, 3, 30, 101089, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b101089-T1Z8bM1jxgEz.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1377, 'Kiratto Pri☆chan', 'キラッとプリ☆チャン', NULL, 'First-year middle school girls Mirai Momoyama and Emo Moegi are two aspiring idols who decide to use the \"Pri☆Chan System,\" a system used by famous people and companies to broadcast content. Like many girls starting their own channels and uploading content, the pair decide to become their own producers, starting their own channel in an attempt to become Pri☆Chan idols.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 29, 1, 24, 51, 101097, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n101097-d0FJRgJJXE32.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1378, 'Beyblade Burst Turbo', 'ベイブレードバースト超セツ', NULL, 'Aiger Akabane is a wild child, who grew up surrounded by nature. Inspired by a chance Bey battle with Valt Aoi, Aiger sets his sights on becoming an invincible Blader with the help of his Turbo Bey, Z Achilles.<br><br>\nBattling powerful opponents and seeking strength; Aiger sets out to defeat Valt and claim the title of World Champion. Here begins Aiger\'s tale of epic adventures and fierce battles on his way to the top.<br><br>(Source: d-rights)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":2,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 45, 1, 23, 51, 101115, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101115-4FLEBjhD8FSJ.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1380, 'ゆるキャン△ OVA', 'null', NULL, 'The official Twitter account for the television anime of Afro\'s Yurucamp (Yurukyan△, Laid-Back Camp Δ) manga revealed on Saturday that the anime\'s first Blu-ray Disc and DVD will feature a \"Yuru Camp Episode 0\" anime on the disc. The anime will tell a story before Nadeshiko joins the club.<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Heya Camp△ Episode 0, Yuru Camp△ Specials', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":28,\"month\":3,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 91, 1, 8, 3, 101206, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101206-wNJoqkQgVsYv.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1383, '若おかみは小学生！', 'null', NULL, 'The \"story of laughter and tears\" centers around \"Okko,\" a sixth-grade elementary school girl who lost her parents in a traffic accident. She moves to her grandmother\'s hot spring inn \"Haru no Ya\" (Spring House) and trains to run the inn. She gradually grows up with the help of the ghost \"Uri-bou\" and other mysterious friends.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Okko\'s Inn', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 8, 1, 12, 24, 101277, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101277-vJbdhlcE57ie.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1384, '黒猫モンロヲ', 'null', NULL, 'The TV shorts follow the black cat Monroe and the human Yoppy and their \"normal and special everyday lives.\"\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":17,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 1, 26, 101279, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/101279-hvotDYsEm2Kt.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1385, '天下統一恋の乱　出陣！雑賀4人衆', 'null', NULL, '15th Century Japan is ravaged by constant wars, as the lords of the realm seek to rule the land. Having lost your father in battle, you are working in the restaurant he left your mother and little brother...when an evil magistrate sends your little brother away...to become a poison taster! To save his life, you disguise yourself as a boy and go to the castle in his place...but what awaits you there is so much more!<br><br>\n\n“I\'ll show you all...my divine rule!”<br><br>\n\nIn the Sengoku era...love is the most dangerous battle of all!<br><br>\n\n(Source: Official Website)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":28,\"month\":5,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 3, 1, NULL, 4, 101290, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx101290-vHdD8XlWtEEd.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1387, 'レディスポ', 'null', NULL, 'The anime is a science-fiction comedy where various pro sports bounty hunters fight each other in sporting events. The story centers on Arigetti, Korupi, and Sabina, three women in a team who participate in various sports.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Lady Sports, Ladyspo The IAM, Ladyspo The Illustrated Animated Movie', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":10,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 2, 1, 4, 12, 101314, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx101314-QFtdDu5u60YW.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1388, 'うさぎのマシュー', 'null', NULL, 'The story centers on Matthew, a daydreaming worrywart of a rabbit. Matthew also has two friends: Keron, a pessimistic frog who is fond of good-luck charms; and Ham, a hamster of few words and who moves through life at his own pace. The story follows the three animals\' everyday lives within a mysterious forest.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Matthew the Rabbit', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 1, 52, 101354, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101354-JOGkgCReDrpy.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
