(1396, '妖怪ウォッチ シャドウサイド', 'null', NULL, 'Keisuke is a fifth grader who does not believe in ghosts, UFOs, or even youkai. Lately, he has noticed that Natsume has been coming home late, and one day decides to tail her. When he discovers that Natsume goes to a youkai detective agency, Natsume is forced to involve Keisuke in her activities.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 11, 1, 24, 49, 101555, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b101555-A0XoGyPyUADx.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1397, 'Aggretsuko', 'アグレッシブ烈子', NULL, 'Some offices have stereotypical dynamics: the chauvinistic pig of a boss who never does any real work; the employees whose goal is to suck up to the boss; the ones whose lives seem perfect; and the individuals who have all the actual work pushed onto them. Retsuko the red panda is in the last group, as she stays late most nights to make up the work her coworkers are too lazy to do themselves.<br>\n<br>\nHer relief from the stress of her everyday life comes in the form of singing death metal at a local karaoke club. Night after night, Retsuko channels her grief into a microphone and considers the place to be her own personal sanctuary. But as she moves further away from her comfort zone and the ideas people have of her, she discovers that letting others into her world of death metal may not be such a bad thing.\n', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":20,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 879, 1, 15, 10, 101571, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101571-ozTDmqA2jHGe.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1398, 'CARDFIGHT!! VANGUARD', 'カードファイト!! ヴァンガード (2018)', NULL, 'The main protagonist Sendou Aichi, is a timid and mundane third-year middle school boy. The thing that supported Aichi\'s heart, was the \"Blaster Blade\" card that he received as a child. It\'s an important rare card from \"Vanguard\", a card game with the imaginary world of \"Planet Cray\" as its stage. From the day he reunited with the person who gave him that card \"Toshiki Kai\", Aichi\'s everyday life began to change.<br><br>(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":5,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 25, 1, 23, 52, 101594, '2021-11-30 11:20:09', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/101594-OkHx6V5XvsIj.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
