(1406, '陰陽師・平安物語', 'null', NULL, 'The courtyard is awash with cherry blossom petals, appearing especially beautiful in the moonlight. Kagura, waking up, sits in the hallway facing the courtyard, \"The courtyard at night, it seems like something can happen at anytime......\"\n<br><br>\nSuddenly a butterfly glides past, its scales glittering - Kochou no Sei. That\'s right, nighttime is indeed suitable for telling stories. \nKagura grows sleepy under the influence of dust - Kochou no Sei. And after Kagura-sama falls asleep - that will be the beginning of the story in the dream!\n', 0, 1, 'Onmyouji: Peace Story, 阴阳师·平安物语, Yin Yang Shi: Ping An Wu Yu', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":21,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 5, 1, 5, 12, 102004, '2021-11-30 11:20:10', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx102004-KtbwGJYZGDtW.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1407, 'Cats and Peachtopia', '猫与桃花源', NULL, 'A cat named Blanket has long been living in a high-rise apartment in the city with his son, Cloak. One day, curious about the outside world, Cloak decides to leave home and embarks on an adventure to find the legendary cat\'s paradise. To find his son, Blanket must overcome his fear and reconcile with his past, with the help of a female Macaw.\n', 0, 1, 'Mao Yu Taohua Yuan, Mao Yu Taohuayuan', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":5,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 105, 1, 102060, '2021-11-30 11:20:10', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/102060-oBFQASKeb1L5.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1408, 'Shibuya Vernacular', 'トキノ交差', NULL, 'A four-dimensional short anime will start at the very beginning of Shibuya Crossing, that is, 10,000 years in the past. The anime is part of a collaborative project helmed by Yoshitoshi Shinomiya. It features a hybrid of animation and live-action. The short was screened on Shibuya\'s Crossing screens and a YouTube-friendly version was posted as well.\n\nThe project also has a crowdfunding campaign to raise 1,800,000 yen (US$16,500) to hold a exhibition of the production materials in Shibuya in mid-August.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Tokino Crossing', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":20,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 1, 1, 1, 1, 102399, '2021-11-30 11:20:10', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/102399-AyM1dpwO8oCD.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1409, 'Utawarerumono: Imperial Princess Tusukuru\'s Splendid Days', 'うたわれるもの トゥスクル皇女の華麗なる日々', NULL, 'Included with the premium collection release of the PS4 remake of Utawarerumono: Chiriyukumono e no Komoriuta. The anime will tell the story of Kuon\'s childhood days.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":26,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 3, 1, 14, 1, 102573, '2021-11-30 11:20:10', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/102573-IOx6G4eYuzQa.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1410, '映画クレヨンしんちゃん 爆盛！カンフーボーイズ ～拉麺大乱～', 'null', NULL, 'Shin-chan is all set to challenge Kung Fu in the Chinatown of Kasukabe city, known as \"Aiya Town\".\nShinnosuke and the Kasukabe Defence Force are going to put up a totally no-stunt Kung Fu challenge on the stage.<br><br>\n\n(Source: Wiki)', 0, 1, 'Shin-chan y los kung-fu boys', 'japan', 'SPRING', 2018, '{\"day\":13,\"month\":4,\"year\":2018}', 'FINISHED', 2, 1, 105, 1, 103690, '2021-11-30 11:20:10', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx103690-zlhPdGJV63jB.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
