(1519, '超游世界 -BEING THE REALITY-', 'null', NULL, 'A world where mysterious beings called \"Disasters\" continually threaten the peace of the world. A special military unit called Saber is formed to oppose Disaster. Private conglomerates and the independent self-defense organization Blade also form, and advance on the enemy. Noii is a high school student who yearns to join Saber and fight Disaster. After a mysterious girl named Motis transfers into his class, his normal life completely changes.\n<p>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Chouyuu Sekai: Being the Reality, World of Super Sand Box: Being the Reality, Chao You Shijie', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":12,\"month\":1,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 19, 1, 12, 20, 98104, '2021-11-30 11:20:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/98104-xrY6ddaWn8pl.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1520, 'スーパーダンガンロンパ2.5 狛枝凪斗と世界の破壊者', 'null', NULL, 'Nagito Komaeda wakes up after experiencing death in the Neo World Program. What kind of world is he seeing and why did he wake up?<br><br>\n\nNagito appears to be in a strange world, including students who have been seen before as well as people who never existed. He is an ordinary boy with no Ultimate Luck, attending an ordinary school. Constrained by being the protagonist, he thinks that having a big talent would interrupt his happiness. He believes that living an ordinary life, being moderately happy, while watching his classmates have a normal youth is what\'s wonderful.<br><br>\n\nHowever, one day, a boy calling himself \"The Destroyer of the World\" appears, having the form of red-eyed Hajime Hinata. He begins the destruction of Nagito\'s world...<br><br>\n\n(Source: Danganronpa Wikia)', 0, 1, 'Super Danganronpa 2.5: Nagito Komaeda and the Destroyer of the World, Super Danganronpa 2.5: Nagito Komaeda and the World Destroyer', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":12,\"month\":1,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 283, 1, 25, 1, 98153, '2021-11-30 11:20:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n98153-zFsTf8XmAkss.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
