(1542, 'きらり輝く', 'null', NULL, 'Tekken is the tourism ambassador for Omachi in the Nagano Prefecture. It is his home town. The short is a story based on men\'s and women\'s romance set within the city and features the Shinano-Omachi Station, the Omachi hot springs village, the Omachi Mountain Museum, etc.\n<br><br>\nTekken stated to Oricon News that it took him 3 months to write the story. The film contains 2381 hand drawn pages.\n', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":29,\"month\":3,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 1, 1, 11, 1, 102457, '2021-11-30 11:20:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/102457-8f5pvi2vkA91.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1543, 'ららマジ', 'null', NULL, 'The opening animation (and promotional video) to Rara Maji, a school girls\' RPG with music, magic, and engaging stories. The game is a co-production between Wright Flyer Studios and A-1 Pictures, the latter also animated the video.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Official site)', 0, 1, 'Lala Maji', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":27,\"month\":1,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 1, 1, 1, 1, 102647, '2021-11-30 11:20:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/102647-pFSZdqdxVMLB.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1544, 'ぼくは知ってるよ。', 'null', NULL, 'A web anime created for the Dotwan dog food company. The episode illustrates the daily life of a family and their dog.\n', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":21,\"month\":6,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 3, 1, 102702, '2021-11-30 11:20:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/102702-qAa7xTMG9u0u.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1545, 'Inazma Delivery', 'イナズマデリバリー', NULL, 'Inazma Delivery is set in the town of Babiden City, where everything runs on electricity. Hemingway is an earnest young man who works at the delivery company Inazma, which promises to deliver any package to its proper destination. One day, an extraterrestrial lost child in a shark costume named Bytheway appears and asks to be delivered to its home planet, and soon Hemingway and Bytheway are embroiled in all sorts of adventures.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":9,\"month\":12,\"year\":2016}', 'FINISHED', 2, 1, 2, 10, 102940, '2021-11-30 11:20:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/nx102940-l9siqs6GxjQU.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1546, 'Kingdom Hearts χ Back Cover', 'キングダム ハーツ キー バックカバー', NULL, 'Long ago, in the \"age of fairy tales,\" the world\'s light is protected by seven individuals who reside in Daybreak Town and wield unique weapons called \"Keyblades\": the Master of Masters and his six apprentices. A devastating conflict has been foreseen, and the world\'s end is imminent. In order to heal it, the Master of Masters gives his disciples unique roles and instructs them to form Unions comprised of other Keyblade wielders. Soon afterwards, the Master vanishes.\n<br><br>\n(Source: KH Wikia)', 0, 1, 'Kingdom Hearts Unchained Key Backcover, Kingdom Hearts Unchained X Backcover', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":12,\"month\":1,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 23, 1, 62, 1, 103441, '2021-11-30 11:20:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/103441-gaWN1Il5Yug6.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1547, '劇場版プリパラ　み～んなでかがやけ！キラリン☆スターライブ！', 'null', NULL, 'Laala and friends go on a \"Puchuu Tour\". They visit various planets around the solar system to spread the word about how wonderful PriPara is, but challenges await on each planet.<br><br>\n\n(Source: PriPara Wiki)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":4,\"month\":3,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 3, 1, 65, 1, 103740, '2021-11-30 11:20:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/n103740-KUsAThtB6UTB.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1548, 'SENGOKUCHOJYUGIGA Season2', '戦国鳥獣戯画～乙～', NULL, 'Second season of <i>Sengoku Choujuu Giga</i>.', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":15,\"month\":1,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 3, 13, 116053, '2021-11-30 11:20:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx116053-AhbYpZvpFQNJ.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1549, 'たまぽんず', 'null', NULL, 'The story follows Mihiro and begins on a day like any other. Mihiro bumps heads with a pet dog and loses consciousness. When she wakes up, she finds herself in a mysterious animal world. Mihiro discovers the shocking truth of her new situation and starts work at an animal pawn shop. She sets her sights on the day she can leave the shop and return to her former world.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":27,\"month\":1,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 1, 1, 4, 6, 116059, '2021-11-30 11:20:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b116059-7GYFwgZ2mTMn.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1550, 'ゴーちゃん。〜モコとちんじゅうの森の仲間たち〜', 'null', NULL, 'Go-chan arrives on earth in search of the heart plasma that will restore peace to his home planet EX Panda. He meets a human girl named Moko, who lives on a farm with her grandfather, and several strange animals called Chinjuumin. They pass their days enjoyably, but trouble begins when humans invade the forest home of the Chinjuumin looking to capture them. Meanwhile, Moko\'s family life gets complicated when her grandmother arrives from the city.<br><br>(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":29,\"month\":1,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 53, 1, 116785, '2021-11-30 11:20:36', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b116785-ZFf3p6EBrpo4.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1551, 'ちぇいん黒にくる!!', 'null', NULL, 'Each television episode of Chain Chronicle: Haecceitas no Hikari aired weekly with one of 12 \"Chein Kuro-Nikuru\", a wordplay on Chain Chronicle\'s Japanese pronunciation and the Japanese term for black shorts.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, 'Chain Chronican Black Shorts', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":1,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 1, 1, 1, 12, 122062, '2021-11-30 11:20:37', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b122062-ZKmgBmx9arpQ.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1552, 'アニメガタリズ: ユクトシ、クルトシ ', 'null', NULL, 'Special short episode of Animegataris streamed on Niconico-douga.', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":31,\"month\":12,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 3, 1, 123056, '2021-11-30 11:20:37', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b123056-hxAJOCWj8A16.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1553, 'Go for 2020', 'null', NULL, 'Studio Colorido was commissioned by Japanese real estate developer Mitsui Fudosan to create a promotional video for their BE THE CHANGE campaign, in anticipation of the Tokyo 2020 Summer Olympic and Paralympic games. Initiatives from the campaign include communal sport academies, promotional city dressing, and the FUTSUJANAI TEN interactive sports exhibition. In particular, the campaign supports sport climbing, wheelchair rugby, and women\'s basketball, the latter of which is featured in the video.', 0, 1, 'Nihonbashi City Dressing for TOKYO 2020, 日本橋シティドレッシング for TOKYO 2020', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":21,\"month\":2,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 4, 1, 126167, '2021-11-30 11:20:37', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/126167-w6LK2frOVgd3.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1554, 'ムーム はじまりの物語', 'null', NULL, 'A prequel to the Moom film which shows Moom coming to life. The short was included on the DVD release of the Moom film.', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":18,\"month\":1,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 4, 1, 126864, '2021-11-30 11:20:37', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b126864-CIC60EHNuRUq.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1555, 'がん がん がんこちゃん', 'null', NULL, 'The anime follows a boy named Gen, who time travels from the year 2020 to a distant future where humanity has gone extinct. He begins staying at the Ganko family home in the Rustling Forest, where he has none of the amenities he is used to: no electricity, gas, or running water, as well as no television, smartphones, convenience stores, snacks, or games.\n<br><br>\n(Source: Anime News Network)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":19,\"month\":12,\"year\":2016}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 5, 10, 126910, '2021-11-30 11:20:37', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx126910-ZFnDotB0NHpp.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1556, 'みどりのくにのおともだち こえだちゃん', 'null', NULL, 'Based on the Takara Tomy toy line.', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":3,\"month\":3,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 3, 8, 127507, '2021-11-30 11:20:37', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b127507-OQgmm7Lv7Xy6.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1557, 'MAFF × ちょびっとづかん', 'null', NULL, 'A series of collaboration episodes between Chobitto Zukan and \nthe Ministry of Agriculture, Forestry and Fisheries.', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":28,\"month\":2,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 0, 1, 1, 4, 130244, '2021-11-30 11:20:37', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b130244-X2c8Wcx81N2B.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1558, 'クレヨンしんちゃん外伝 家族連れ狼', 'null', NULL, 'Master butt-swordsman Hiroshinosuke Nohara (Lone Wolf) travels with his family seeking employment. The family encounters a mysterious girl Hazumi and a wild dog Shiro, and decides to travel together. The group is attacked by various assassins, eventually their lives are threatened by the butt-swordsmen\'s enemy, the armpit-swordsmen of the Demon Bull Clan. Who will win: butts or armpits? Against an array of idiosyncratic enemies, Hiroshinosuke Nohara and his son Shinnosuke have the chance to display their swashbuckling skills.\n<br><br>\n(Source: ANN)', 0, 1, '', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2017, '{\"day\":22,\"month\":2,\"year\":2017}', 'FINISHED', 1, 1, 7, 13, 139037, '2021-11-30 11:20:37', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b139037-0VI5I8YBHizi.jpg', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo'),
(1601, 'Kizumonogatari Part 1: Tekketsu', '傷物語〈Ⅰ鉄血篇〉', NULL, 'First season of the Monogatari Series, part 2/6. Contains the arc Koyomi Vamp from the Kizumonogatari light novel. \n<br><br>\nMarch 25th—just another day during spring break. Koyomi Araragi, a second year high school student at Naoetsu High School, befriends Tsubasa Hanekawa, the top honors student at his school. Hanekawa mentions a rumor about a \"blonde vampire\" that has been sighted around their town recently. Araragi, who is usually anti-social, takes a liking to her down-to-earth personality.\n<br><br>\nThat night, Araragi encounters the rumored vampire: she is Kiss-Shot Acerola-Orion Heart-Under-Blade, also known as the \"iron-blooded, hot-blooded, cold-blooded King of Apparitions.\" The stunningly beautiful vampire cries out for Koyomi to save her as she lies in a pool of her own blood, all four of her limbs cut off. Kiss-shot asks Araragi to give her his blood, and when he does, the next moment he awakes, Araragi finds himself reborn as her vampire kin. As Araragi struggles to accept his existence, Kiss-Shot whispers, \"Welcome to the world of darkness...\"\n<br><br>\n(Source: Aniplex)', 2, 1, 'Wound Tale 1: Iron Blood', 'japan', 'WINTER', 2016, '{\"day\":8,\"month\":1,\"year\":2016}', 'FINISHED', 2476, 1, 64, 1, 9260, '2021-11-30 11:21:02', 'https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/9260-pWGH4aPINpiw.png', '2021-12-07 02:52:32', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/lbunPmtDPJo');
